{"type":"message","id":"e7c481f5","parentId":"65c74ab0","timestamp":"2026-06-01T02:33:15.640Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The owner wants me to show the list of skills I've learned. Let me check what skills I have available and what I've documented in my memory/notes.\n\nFrom the available_skills at the top, I can see these built-in/plugin skills:\n1. feishu-doc - Feishu document read/write\n2. feishu-drive - Feishu cloud storage\n3. feishu-perm - Feishu permission management\n4. feishu-wiki - Feishu knowledge base\n5. skill-creator - Create/edit skill files\n6. taskflow - Coordinate multi-step tasks\n7. taskflow-inbox-triage - Inbox triage pattern\n\nAnd from my MEMORY.md and TOOLS.md, I've developed custom workflows:\n\n1. **GitLab 权限管理** (gitlab-permission) - 管理 GitLab 项目成员权限\n2. **TAPD 自动提单** (tapd-bug-create) - 自动创建缺陷单\n3. **1V1 VSMODE 需求单** (tapd-vsmode-story) - 创建 1v1 需求单\n4. **更新测试服** (热更流水线) - Unity 客户端热更\n5. **更新服务器** (DevOps) - .NET 服务端更新\n6. **登录保活** - TAPD/DevOps/GitLab 自动保活\n7. **飞书群消息发送** - 通过 API 发群消息\n8. **OpenClaw 网关自助重启** - 延迟重启网关\n\nLet me also check the skills-manifest to see version info.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_jLc25EZkJEfUJjm2LeLO7845","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace\\memory\\skills-manifest.json"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":6885,"output":416,"cacheRead":13824,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":21125,"cost":{"input":0.0009639000000000001,"output":0.00011648000000000001,"cacheRead":0.00038707199999999997,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0014674520000000002}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780281191370,"responseId":"37fe692e-8696-4887-be6c-462fb8a4a056"}}
{"type":"message","id":"3aa4e7c0","parentId":"e7c481f5","timestamp":"2026-06-01T02:33:15.851Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_00_jLc25EZkJEfUJjm2LeLO7845","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"gitlab-permission\": {\n    \"version\": 3,\n    \"updatedAt\": \"2026-05-22T10:57:00.000Z\",\n    \"description\": \"GitLab 权限管理，默认权限 Reporter(20)\"\n  },\n  \"tapd-bug-create\": {\n    \"version\": 1,\n    \"updatedAt\": \"2026-05-18T00:00:00.000Z\",\n    \"description\": \"TAPD 自动提单\"\n  },\n  \"tapd-vsmode-story\": {\n    \"version\": 1,\n    \"updatedAt\": \"2026-05-20T00:00:00.000Z\",\n    \"description\": \"1V1 VSMODE 需求单\"\n  },\n  \"solo-config-field\": {\n    \"version\": 1,\n    \"updatedAt\": \"2026-05-26T07:33:00.000Z\",\n    \"description\": \"SoloConfig Luban 表格字段添加\"\n  }\n}\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1780281195851}}
{"type":"message","id":"fa8ce50f","parentId":"3aa4e7c0","timestamp":"2026-06-01T02:33:19.453Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I have a comprehensive picture. Let me present a clean summary of all my skills/capabilities.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"🌸 主人，以下是目前掌握的全部技能：\n\n**📦 安装的技能插件**\n| 技能 | 能力 |\n|------|------|\n| `feishu-doc` | 飞书文档读写 |\n| `feishu-drive` | 飞书云盘文件管理 |\n| `feishu-perm` | 飞书文档/文件权限管理 |\n| `feishu-wiki` | 飞书知识库导航 |\n| `skill-creator` | 创建/编辑 AgentSkill |\n| `taskflow` | 多步骤持久化任务编排 |\n| `taskflow-inbox-triage` | 收件箱分流处理 |\n\n**🧠 自研工作流**\n| 技能 | 版本 | 能力 |\n|------|------|------|\n| `gitlab-permission` | v3 | GitLab 项目管理、成员增删改、默认 Reporter |\n| `tapd-bug-create` | v1 | 自动创建缺陷单（含附件上传、@人） |\n| `tapd-vsmode-story` | v1 | 提 1v1 需求单（6种模板：client/server/design/ui/motion/audio） |\n| `solo-config-field` | v1 | SoloConfig Luban 表格字段添加 |\n\n**🔧 自动化流水线**\n| 流水线 | 本质 | 耗时 |\n|--------|------|------|\n| **更新测试服** | Unity 热更（打资源+上传CDN） | ~几分钟 |\n| **更新服务器** | DevOps 编译 .NET + 重启微服务 | ~几分钟 |\n| **登录保活** | TAPD/DevOps/GitLab 每天自动续期 | 后台跑 |\n\n**🛠️ 小工具**\n- 飞书群消息发送（`feishu_send_group.mjs`）\n- OpenClaw 网关延迟重启（`restart_gateway.ps1`）\n\n主人有什么需要调用的直接说~"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":237,"output":448,"cacheRead":21120,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":21805,"cost":{"input":0.000033180000000000004,"output":0.00012544000000000002,"cacheRead":0.00059136,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00074998}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1780281195852,"responseId":"eb2fc428-be2d-4066-984a-caedf11043f2"}}
