{"type":"message","id":"457b5f5a","parentId":"857b441d","timestamp":"2026-06-01T02:53:19.973Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The owner is sharing some Unity build errors/warnings. These seem to be Android build related issues. Let me analyze them:\n\n1. `android.enableR8=false` is deprecated and will be removed in AGP 5.0 - this is just a warning about a deprecated Gradle setting\n2. `Exception while marshalling ... package.xml. Probably the SDK is read-only` - Two files in the Unity Android SDK cannot be marshalled because they appear to be read-only. These are in Unity's built-in Android SDK at `C:\\Program Files\\Unity\\Hub\\Editor\\2020.3.49f1-x86_64\\Editor\\Data\\PlaybackEngines\\AndroidPlayer\\SDK\\build-tools\\30.0.2\\package.xml` and `platform-tools\\package.xml`.\n\nThe owner seems to be sharing this as a problem they encountered (probably during an Android build). Let me provide analysis and potential fixes.\n\nThis is just the owner sharing an error output - probably copy-pasted from a Unity build log. Let me respond helpfully.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"🌸 主人，这是打 Android 包报的错？两个问题分析下：\n\n**1️⃣ `android.enableR8=false` 警告**\n无视就好，Unity 2020.3 自带的 AGP 还用不了 R8，等升引擎再处理。\n\n**2️⃣ SDK package.xml 只读异常（这是关键）**\n```\nException while marshalling ... package.xml. Probably the SDK is read-only\n```\nUnity 内置的 Android SDK 在 `Program Files` 下，系统默认是只读权限，Gradle 没法写入 `package.xml`。解决方案：\n\n**方案 A（推荐）：改 SDK 目录权限**\n```powershell\n# 给当前用户加上写入权限\nicacls \"C:\\Program Files\\Unity\\Hub\\Editor\\2020.3.49f1-x86_64\\Editor\\Data\\PlaybackEngines\\AndroidPlayer\\SDK\" /grant \"Everyone:(OI)(CI)W\" /T\n```\n\n**方案 B：让 Unity 用外部 SDK**\nUnity → Preferences → External Tools → Android SDK — 把路径指到用户目录下可写的 SDK（比如 `C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\Android\\Sdk`）\n\n**方案 C：直接给两个文件加写权限**\n```powershell\nicacls \"C:\\Program Files\\Unity\\Hub\\Editor\\2020.3.49f1-x86_64\\Editor\\Data\\PlaybackEngines\\AndroidPlayer\\SDK\\build-tools\\30.0.2\\package.xml\" /grant \"Everyone:W\"\nicacls \"C:\\Program Files\\Unity\\Hub\\Editor\\2020.3.49f1-x86_64\\Editor\\Data\\PlaybackEngines\\AndroidPlayer\\SDK\\platform-tools\\package.xml\" /grant \"Everyone:W\"\n```\n\n要我现在跑一下方案 A 处理掉？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":2428,"output":629,"cacheRead":19584,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":22641,"cost":{"input":0.00033992,"output":0.00017612000000000001,"cacheRead":0.000548352,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.001064392}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1780282394267,"responseId":"2278d6e3-89bd-4f43-8524-87b100b88479"}}
