{"type":"message","id":"b01e3fbe","parentId":"d5e042ed","timestamp":"2026-06-01T02:54:19.689Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Elevated is not available for Feishu channel. I'll ask the owner to run it manually from their terminal, or suggest they use a different approach.\n\nThe owner can't run elevated from here. Let me tell them to run the command themselves in an admin PowerShell.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"🌸 当前环境没法提权操作，主人需要自己在 **管理员 PowerShell** 里跑一下：\n\n```powershell\nicacls \"C:\\Program Files\\Unity\\Hub\\Editor\\2020.3.49f1-x86_64\\Editor\\Data\\PlaybackEngines\\AndroidPlayer\\SDK\" /grant \"Everyone:(OI)(CI)W\" /T\n```\n\n或者如果嫌麻烦，还有个更简单的替代方案——去 **Unity Preferences → External Tools → Android SDK**，把 SDK 路径改成用户目录下可写的位置就行了，不用动 `Program Files` 的权限。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":231,"output":185,"cacheRead":22784,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":23200,"cost":{"input":0.000032340000000000005,"output":0.000051800000000000005,"cacheRead":0.000637952,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.000722092}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1780282457479,"responseId":"922211c4-b877-4601-9d1c-1a2313d3cacd"}}
