{"type":"message","id":"c0c5f364","parentId":"e7d0199f","timestamp":"2026-06-01T06:24:44.942Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The owner wants to update the 1v1 test server. According to TOOLS.md and MEMORY.md:\n\n\"更新1v1_测试服务器\" - This is the server-side DevOps pipeline update. The dest value is \"1v1_test\".\n\nLet me check the flow:\n1. Check DevOps Cookie is valid\n2. Use Playwright to open the pipeline page, click \"启动新构建\"\n3. Change dest to \"1v1_test\", keep other variables default\n4. Submit, confirm building\n5. Notify the owner when done\n\nThis is a >10s task, so I should spawn a sub-agent to handle it in the background.\n\nThe DevOps pipeline ID is `p-f78c977835c84b71a6d58b4746cd1c4a`.\n\nLet me spawn a sub-agent to handle this.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"好的主人，开始更新 1v1_test 服，我来开个子任务跑 DevOps 流水线。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_CUwvDy4sFaIixZ6OwrnD4782","name":"sessions_spawn","arguments":{"task":"执行 1v1 服务器更新 DevOps 流水线，dest=1v1_test。\n\n## 流程\n1. 检查 DevOps Cookie 是否有效（`workspace/devops_cookies.json`）\n2. 用 Playwright（headed 模式，因为属于交互操作）打开 DevOps 流水线页面，点击「启动新构建」\n3. dest 改为 `1v1_test`，其他变量保持默认\n4. 提交触发，确认构建进入运行中\n5. 等待构建完成（轮询构建状态）\n6. 完成后通过 sessions_send 通知主人结果（session key 用 \"main\" 或者 \"ou_6509d346e8d50ef882f89c436e6c977f\"）\n\n## 重要提示\n- 流水线页面 URL 根据 MEMORY.md，Pipeline ID 为 `p-f78c977835c84b71a6d58b4746cd1c4a`\n- 需要用到 Playwright，脚本在 `workspace/scripts/` 下\n- DevOps 登录 Cookie 在 `workspace/devops_cookies.json`\n- 本次任务是主人 Yousan(叶枝君) 发起的，完成后直接通知他\n- 反馈用 dest 值：`1v1_test`\n\n执行完发送结果给主 session（主人是 ou_6509d346e8d50ef882f89c436e6c977f 的私聊）。","mode":"run"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":1487,"output":571,"cacheRead":21760,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":23818,"cost":{"input":0.00020818,"output":0.00015988000000000002,"cacheRead":0.00060928,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0009773400000000002}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timesta