{"type":"message","id":"2aabebe9","parentId":"c691e699","timestamp":"2026-06-01T06:34:21.185Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"So the sub-agent found that DevOps cookies have expired (last refreshed May 20, 12 days ago). Feishu SSO didn't work either. The sub-agent has already yielded a message asking the user to re-login. Let me relay this to the user in a concise way.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"🌸 DevOps 登录过期了，1v1_test 服没更新成。\n\n**原因：** DevOps Cookie 欠保活 12 天了（上次是 5/20），飞书 SSO 也自动登不上。\n\n**方案 A：** 我开 headed 浏览器，主人扫飞书码登录一下就行。要试试吗？\n\n**方案 B：** 主人自己在 Chrome 里登一次 DevOps 流水线页，然后告诉我说登好了，我直接从 Chrome 抓 Cookie。链接在这：\n<https://devops.devcloud.ztgame.com/projects/yyzy/pipelines/p-f78c977835c84b71a6d58b4746cd1c4a>"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":19829,"output":212,"cacheRead":24320,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":44361,"cost":{"input":0.0027760600000000003,"output":0.00005936,"cacheRead":0.00068096,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0035163800000000004}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1780295657469,"responseId":"cb7ee6bb-b02f-46a8-ad83-89950018cf41"}}
