{"type":"message","id":"156bebaa","parentId":"19d94e9e","timestamp":"2026-06-01T06:40:51.706Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The owner sent me the fresh DevOps cookies from Chrome. I need to:\n1. Save these cookies to `workspace/devops_cookies.json`\n2. Then trigger the 1v1_test DevOps pipeline\n\nLet me first save the cookies and then spawn a sub-agent to trigger the pipeline.\n\nActually, these cookies are in Chrome's export format (different structure). I need to convert them to Playwright-compatible format. The Chrome format has `domain`, `name`, `value`, `httpOnly`, `secure`, `session`, `expirationDate`, `hostOnly`, `sameSite`, `path`, `storeId`.\n\nPlaywright expects: `name`, `value`, `domain`, `path`, `httpOnly`, `secure`, `sameSite`, `expires`.\n\nLet me just convert the format and save.\n\nThen I'll need to use Playwright to open the pipeline page, click \"启动新构建\", change dest to \"1v1_test\", and submit.\n\nLet me write the cookies first and then spawn a sub-agent.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"主人登好了，我来写 Cookie 然后触发流水线。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_G4tHfTdk5nnHDpPcRVsn7268","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace\\devops_cookies.json","content":"[\n  {\n    \"name\": \"devops_return_url\",\n    \"value\": \"https://devops.devcloud.ztgame.com/projects/yyzy/pipelines/p-f78c977835c84b71a6d58b4746cd1c4a\",\n    \"domain\": \".devcloud.ztgame.com\",\n    \"path\": \"/\",\n    \"httpOnly\": false,\n    \"secure\": false,\n    \"sameSite\": \"None\",\n    \"expires\": 1780382398\n  },\n  {\n    \"name\": \"devops_token\",\n    \"value\": \"eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiJ9.eyJleHAiOjE3ODAzODI0MDMsInVzZXJfbmFtZSI6InllemhpanVuIn0.O5U10SOnXDR2Q02ZDOxG47hV3VAv65y09yDaZ-AO-bY\",\n    \"domain\": \".devcloud.ztgame.com\",\n    \"path\": \"/\",\n    \"httpOnly\": false,\n    \"secure\": false,\n    \"sameSite\": \"None\",\n    \"expires\": 1780382404.043704\n  }