{"type":"message","id":"f0a0f9fe","parentId":"f39425ac","timestamp":"2026-06-01T06:40:56.468Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now let me check if the cookies actually work. First let me verify by trying to access the DevOps page with these cookies. But actually, let me just spawn a sub-agent that will use Playwright to trigger the pipeline.\n\nThe task:\n1. Load the new cookies from `devops_cookies.json`\n2. Open the pipeline page: `https://devops.devcloud.ztgame.com/projects/yyzy/pipelines/p-f78c977835c84b71a6d58b4746cd1c4a`\n3. Click \"启动新构建\"\n4. Change dest to `1v1_test`\n5. Submit\n6. Wait for build to complete\n7. Notify the owner\n\nLet me spawn a sub-agent.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_CxEOCFaBulKS5i7pzJuG1556","name":"sessions_spawn","arguments":{"mode":"run","task":"## 任务：触发 1v1_test DevOps 流水线\n\nCookie 已经刷好了，存在 `workspace/devops_cookies.json`。\n\n### 流水线信息\n- **流水线页面：** `https://devops.devcloud.ztgame.com/projects/yyzy/pipelines/p-f78c977835c84b71a6d58b4746cd1c4a`\n- **项目：** yyzy\n- **dest 目标：** `1v1_test`\n\n### 步骤\n1. **验证 Cookie 是否有效**\n   - 用 Playwright（headless: true）加载 `devops_cookies.json`\n   - 访问流水线页面\n   - 确认页面没有跳转到登录页（URL 不含 login/auth），否则报错退出\n\n2. **触发流水线**\n   - 点击「启动新构建」或等效按钮\n   - 找到 dest 参数（可能是下拉选择或输入框），改成 `1v1_test`\n   - 其他参数保持默认\n   - 提交触发\n   - 确认流水线进入运行中状态\n\n3. **等待完成**\n   - 轮询流水线构建状态，直到完成（成功或失败）\n   - 等待时间最多 10 分钟\n\n4. **通知结果**\n   - 用 sessions_send 通知主人（main session）\n   - 告知构建成功/失败\n\n### 注意\n- 用 headless 模式即可\n- 如果 cookie 无效，报错退出让主人知道\n- 这是一个私聊任务（主人是 Yousan 叶枝君）"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":130,"output":562,"cacheRead":30976,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":31668,"cost":{"input":0.000018200000000000002,"output":0.00015736,"cacheRead":0.000867328,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.001042888}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780296051946,"responseId":"c75611f4-6008-4808-95aa-0203e2680