{"type":"message","id":"40105884","parentId":"fc5d959d","timestamp":"2026-06-01T06:42:06.263Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The owner wants me to add DevOps to the keepalive list. Currently HEARTBEAT.md already has DevOps keepalive configured, but it seems it's been failing recently (the DevOps cookie expired). Let me check what's happening.\n\nLooking at the HEARTBEAT.md, DevOps keepalive is already there:\n```\n### DevOps 保活\n- 状态文件：`memory/devops-keepalive-state.json`\n- 脚本：`node scripts/devops_keepalive.mjs`\n```\n\nAnd looking at the MEMORY.md:\n```\n## DevOps 登录保活（2026-05-19）\n- **保活脚本：** `workspace/scripts/devops_keepalive.mjs`\n```\n\nBut the issue is that the DevOps keepalive has been failing because:\n1. The keepalive script itself needs cookies to work - if cookies expire, the script can't refresh them\n2. The last successful DevOps keepalive was May 20, which is 12 days ago\n\nLet me check the current DevOps keepalive state to understand what happened.\n\nActually, the owner just said \"加入保活列表\" - this is because DevOps cookies expired since it wasn't being kept alive. The keepalive script exists in HEARTBEAT.md but maybe it's not running properly or the heartbeat hasn't been checking it.\n\nLet me check the keepalive state to understand the pattern.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_zU4QO8G8Uzd1eJrN3bj62741","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace\\memory\\devops-keepalive-state.json"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_01_5tLkNBThcR4vyL3Neccu2908","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace\\HEARTBEAT.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":7509,"output":411,"cacheRead":24448,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":32368,"cost":{"input":0.00105126,"output":0.00011508,"cacheRead":0.0006845439999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0018508840000000001}},"stop