{"type":"message","id":"266d9153","parentId":"40105884","timestamp":"2026-06-01T06:42:06.474Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_00_zU4QO8G8Uzd1eJrN3bj62741","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"ok\": true,\n  \"at\": \"2026-05-20T03:39:35.522Z\",\n  \"cookieCount\": 25,\n  \"title\": \"流水线 / 流水线列表 巨人 DevOps\"\n}"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1780296126474}}
{"type":"message","id":"de79c8d3","parentId":"266d9153","timestamp":"2026-06-01T06:42:06.475Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_01_5tLkNBThcR4vyL3Neccu2908","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# Heartbeat Tasks\n\n## 登录保活（每天一次）\n\n每天检查保活状态文件，如果距离上次执行 > 20 小时则自动执行。\n\n### TAPD 保活（双账号）\n\n- 周以天（提单用）：`node scripts/tapd_keepalive.mjs`（默认）\n  - Cookie：`tapd_cookies_zhouyitian.json`\n  - 状态：`memory/tapd-keepalive-state-zhouyitian.json`\n- 叶枝君：`node scripts/tapd_keepalive.mjs yezhijun`\n  - Cookie：`tapd_cookies_yezhijun.json`\n  - 状态：`memory/tapd-keepalive-state-yezhijun.json`\n- 两个账号每天都要跑一次保活\n- 退出码：\n  - `0` → ✅ 成功续期\n  - `1` → ❌ 需要重新扫码登录 TAPD，**主动通知主人**\n  - `2` → ⚠️ 脚本错误，记录到当天 memory 文件\n- Cookie：`workspace/tapd_cookies.json`\n\n### DevOps 保活\n\n- 状态文件：`memory/devops-keepalive-state.json`\n- 脚本：`node scripts/devops_keepalive.mjs`\n- 退出码：\n  - `0` → ✅ 成功续期\n  - `1` → ❌ 需要重新登录 DevOps，**主动通知主人**\n  - `2` → ⚠️ 脚本错误，记录到当天 memory 文件\n- Cookie：`workspace/devops_cookies.json`\n\n### GitLab 保活\n\n- 状态文件：`memory/gitlab-keepalive-state.json`\n- 脚本：`node scripts/gitlab_keepalive.mjs`\n- 退出码：\n  - `0` → ✅ 成功续期（Cookie + CSRF Token）\n  - `1` → ❌ 需要重新登录 GitLab（SSO），**主动通知主人**\n  - `2` → ⚠️ 脚本错误，记录到当天 memory 文件\n- Cookie：`workspace/gitlab_cookies.json`\n- CSRF：`workspace/gitlab_csrf.json`\n\n**保活原理：** 访问一次页面，服务器端 session 会自动续期，同时提取新 CSRF Token。\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1780296126474}}
{"type":"message","id":"2815dca8","parentId":"de79c8d3","timestamp":"2026-06-01T06:42:10.979Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"OK so DevOps keepalive IS already in HEARTBEAT.md, and the last successful keepalive was on 2026-05-20. That's 12 days ago.\n\nThe problem is likely that the heartbeat script fails silently when cookies expire, or the heartbeat itself hasn't been running. Let me check what happens.\n\nActually, looking at the keepalive script output from the sub-agent's history - the keepalive script (`devops_keepalive.mjs`) takes existing cookies, visits the page, and if the page redirects to login, it writes `{ ok: false, error: 'session_expired' }` and exits with code 1.\n\nSo the heartbeat ran the script, it failed with code 1 (session_expired), and according to HEARTBEAT.md, when exit code is 1, it should \"主动通知主人\". But it obviously didn't notify or something went wrong.\n\nThe owner is saying \"加入保活列表\" - meaning they want DevOps to be properly kept alive now that we have fresh cookies. \n\nLet me:\n1. First run the keepalive script now with the new cookies to refresh it\n2. Update the keepalive state\n3. Maybe adjust the heartbeat mechanism so DevOps actually gets checked\n\nActually, let me just run the DevOps keepalive script now with the fresh cookies to establish a new baseline.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"好的主人，现在 Cookie 刚刷新的，我先跑一次保活建立基线，这样以后每天自动续期。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_5ksKVXLm4e1mwRTnX7xL2084","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace && node scripts/devops_keepalive.mjs","timeout":45}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":705,"output":397,"cacheRead":32256,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":33358,"cost":{"input":0.0000987,"output":0.00011116000000000001,"cacheRead":0.000903168,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.001113028}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780296126476