{"type":"message","id":"9a9a3024","parentId":"078fb09f","timestamp":"2026-06-01T06:42:16.903Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_00_5DcUnXNR7dsF17H5jFc41521","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[2026-06-01T06:42:13.327Z] Loaded 2 cookies\n[2026-06-01T06:42:13.538Z] Visiting DevOps pipelines page...\n[2026-06-01T06:42:16.753Z] HTTP 200 | url=https://keycloak.devcloud.ztgame.com/auth/realms/giant/protocol/openid-connect/auth?client_id=devops&response_type=code&redirect_uri=https%3A%2F%2Fdevops.devcloud.ztgame.com%2Fms%2Flogin%2Fapi%2Fuser%2Flogin&state=https%3A%2F%2Fdevops.devcloud.ztgame.com%2Fprojects%2Fyyzy%2Fpipelines | title=员工登录-巨人网络\n[2026-06-01T06:42:16.754Z] Body preview: 域帐号\n密码\n通过 飞书 登录\n\n1. 密码丢失请使用 忘记密码；\n\n2. 账号问题请在飞书联系 IT 服务专员；\n\n3. 接入单点登录请使用 开发者平台；\n[2026-06-01T06:42:16.754Z] ❌ Session EXPIRED - need re-login\n\n(Command exited with code 1)"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":1,"durationMs":3993,"aggregated":"[2026-06-01T06:42:13.327Z] Loaded 2 cookies\n[2026-06-01T06:42:13.538Z] Visiting DevOps pipelines page...\n[2026-06-01T06:42:16.753Z] HTTP 200 | url=https://keycloak.devcloud.ztgame.com/auth/realms/giant/protocol/openid-connect/auth?client_id=devops&response_type=code&redirect_uri=https%3A%2F%2Fdevops.devcloud.ztgame.com%2Fms%2Flogin%2Fapi%2Fuser%2Flogin&state=https%3A%2F%2Fdevops.devcloud.ztgame.com%2Fprojects%2Fyyzy%2Fpipelines | title=员工登录-巨人网络\n[2026-06-01T06:42:16.754Z] Body preview: 域帐号\n密码\n通过 飞书 登录\n\n1. 密码丢失请使用 忘记密码；\n\n2. 账号问题请在飞书联系 IT 服务专员；\n\n3. 接入单点登录请使用 开发者平台；\n[2026-06-01T06:42:16.754Z] ❌ Session EXPIRED - need re-login\n\n(Command exited with code 1)","cwd":"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1780296136903}}
{"type":"message","id":"82c31bed","parentId":"9a9a3024","timestamp":"2026-06-01T06:42:26.629Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The just-saved 2 cookies (`devops_return_url` and `devops_token`) are not enough - they got redirected to Keycloak login. The `devops_token` is a JWT that seems to have already expired (the expiration is in the JWT claim: `exp`: `1780382403` which is... let me calculate).\n\n1780382403 - let me convert: 1780382403 / 86400 = 20606.xxx which from Jan 1 1970... Actually the epoch is:\n1780382403 is about June 1, 2026 ~ 14:40 UTC = 22:40 CST. Wait, it's currently June 1 14:42 CST = 06:42 UTC. The token expires at 1780382403 which is... \n\n1780382403 - 1780380000 (roughly June 1 06:00 UTC) = 2403 seconds = 40 minutes. So it expires ~40 minutes from the current timestamp.\n\nActually wait, let me re-check. The current time is around 14:42 CST = 06:42 UTC on June 1, 2026.\nThe expiration in the cookie was 1780382404.043704.\n\nUnix epoch 1780382404 = roughly... let me calculate.\nCurrent Unix time for 2026-06-01 06:42 UTC is approximately:\n2026-01-01 = 1767225600\n2026-06-01 00:00 UTC = 1767225600 + 151 days * 86400 = 1767225600 + 13046400 = 1780272000\n06:42 UTC = 1780272000 + 24120 = 1780296120\n\nSo the current time is ~1780296120 and the token expires at 1780382404. That's a difference of 86284 seconds = about 24 hours. So the token should be valid for 24 hours.\n\nBut it still redirected to login. The issue might be that when we only have 2 cookies (devops_return_url and devops_token), the Keycloak session cookie is missing, so it can't complete the SSO flow.\n\nLet me look at what the user provided vs what we need. The user sent 2 cookies from Chrome. But maybe there are more cookies needed - like the Keycloak session cookie.\n\nActually, the keepalive script needs to have the cookies in the right format to work. The 2 cookies the user sent might not include a Keycloak session. Let me check - the user was already logged into DevOps in their Chrome browser. The script tries to use the cookies it has, but it's lacking the Keycloak session cookie (AUTH_SESSION_ID or similar from keycloak.devcloud.ztgame.com).\n\nI need the user to export ALL cookies from Chrome for the DevOps domains, not just the 2 they sent. Or I need a different approach.\n\nActually, let me look at this from a different angle. The owner said \"加入保活列表\". Maybe they're saying they'll manually keep the session alive by visiting DevOps occasionally, and I just need to make sure the existing scripts are configured properly.\n\nOr maybe they want me to handle this differently - perhaps by using the Chrome user data directory approach instead of relying on cookie files.\n\nLet me think about this more practically:\n1. The user logged into DevOps in Chrome manually\n2. Chrome has all the needed cookies for devcloud.ztgame.com and keycloak.devcloud.ztgame.com\n3. We need to use those cookies\n\nThe most reliable approach would be to extract Chrome cookies for the relevant domains. Let me check if there's an extract script.\n\nActually, I think the practical solution here is:\n1. Ask the user to export ALL cookies for `.devcloud.ztgame.com` and `.keycloak.devcloud.ztgame.com` from Chrome\n2. Or, use a Playwright script with Chrome's user data directory\n3. Or, go back to using the approach of having the user manually visit DevOps once a day\n\nLet me think... the `devops_keepalive.mjs` script tries to refresh the session. But it only has the devops cookies, not the Keycloak session cookies. To properly refresh, you need the Keycloak SSO session cookies too.\n\nActually wait - the original devops_cookies.json had 25 cookies before. Those probably included keycloak cookies. Let me check.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"只靠那 2 个 DevOps 的 JWT 不够，Keycloak 的认证 session 没有带过来，被跳转到登录页了。\n\n主人方便把 Chrome 里 `devcloud.ztgame.com` 和 `keycloak.devcloud.ztgame.com` 两个域名的 **所有 Cookie** 都导出来给我吗？只要贴这俩域名的就行。\n\n或者更简单——我直接用 Playwright 开 headed 模式连 Chrome 的 user data 目录登录一次。主人想走哪条路？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":349,"output":1060,"cacheRead":33536,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":34945,"cost":{"input":0.00004886,"output":0.0002968,"cacheRead":0.000939008,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.001284668}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1780296136905,"responseId":"a81d41e0-11a6-462d-8910-70237b0bfb33"}}
