{"type":"message","id":"a74fa2b4","parentId":"97f89692","timestamp":"2026-06-01T06:43:17.760Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The owner wants me to open a Playwright headed browser so they can log into DevOps in real-time. But this is a Feishu chat - they won't see the browser. \n\nWait, looking at the previous sub-agent's attempt, it tried the headed approach but on the server. The owner is on their own machine. So the browser would open on the server machine (zt-c600365), not the owner's machine.\n\nThe owner probably doesn't realize this - they think Playwright headed mode will open a browser they can see. But the agent runs on the server.\n\nActually, let me reconsider. Maybe I should use a different approach. Let me write a script that:\n1. Opens Chrome via Playwright in headed mode (this will pop up on the server machine)\n2. Navigates to DevOps login page\n3. Waits for the user to scan a QR code or complete login\n4. Then saves the cookies\n\nBut the owner can't see the server machine's screen...\n\nActually, wait. Let me think about this differently. Maybe I should try using `--user-data-dir` with Playwright to connect to the user's Chrome profile on their local machine? No, that won't work because the agent runs on a remote machine.\n\nThe most practical approach might be to create a script that:\n1. Uses Playwright headed mode on the server\n2. Opens the DevOps login page\n3. Takes screenshots periodically so the user can see progress\n4. Since the login page shows \"通过飞书登录\" option, maybe we can use that and the QR code approach\n\nActually, looking at the login page text from the sub-agent's attempt:\n```\n域帐号 密码 通过 飞书 登录\n```\n\nSo there's a \"通过飞书登录\" option. If we click that, it would redirect to Feishu OAuth. But the Feishu session is also expired.\n\nHmm, let me think about another approach. What if we use `devops_refresh_login.mjs` that was created earlier? That script was already written by the previous sub-agent. Let me check if it exists.\n\nActually, the previous sub-agent started writing that script but it was truncated. Let me create a proper script that:\n1. Opens headed browser\n2. Goes to DevOps\n3. If redirected to login, clicks \"通过飞书登录\" \n4. Takes screenshots so I can show them to the user\n5. If it shows a QR code, send the image to the user\n6. After login, saves cookies\n\nBut this is complex. Let me just be honest with the owner - the headed browser opens on the server, they can't physically see it. Let me suggest an alternative.\n\nActually, wait - the owner said \"开playwright\". Maybe they want me to write a script that opens headed mode and they'll find a way, or maybe they just want me to try the \"通过飞书登录\" path. \n\nLet me reconsider the sub-agent that's already running for the pipeline. That sub-agent was trying to use the devops_refresh_login script. Let me check if that sub-agent has already completed.\n\nActually, the first sub-agent completed (failed due to expired cookies), and I spawned a second sub-agent to trigger the pipeline with the new cookies. Let me check the status of the second sub-agent.\n\nActually let me just try a practical approach: the owner says \"开playwright\" - they want me to open headed Playwright. On a server, headed mode opens a visible Chrome window. If the owner has remote desktop access to the server (zt-c600365), they can see it. Let me try anyway.\n\nActually, a better approach: let me write a script that uses headed Playwright, and I'll take screenshots and send them to the user so they can see what's happening. If there's a QR code, I can capture and send it.\n\nActually, looking at the Keycloak login page more carefully from the previous sub-agent's output:\n```\n域帐号 密码 通过 飞书 登录\n```\n\nThere's a \"通过飞书登录\" button. If the user clicks that, it may redirect them to Feishu which could use the existing Feishu session. The Feishu cookies from the browser context might be... actually, the sub-agent already tried this and it failed because the Feishu session cookies weren't available.\n\nLet me take a step back and think about what's really the simplest approach:\n\n1. The user is actively chatting with me on Feishu\n2. Feishu has its own session \n3. If I open a headed browser and navigate to DevOps, click \"通过飞书登录\", it should redirect to Feishu OAuth\n4. Since the user is on Feishu right now, maybe the Feishu OAuth will automatically authenticate because Feishu knows their session\n5. Or, the OAuth will show a QR code or redirect with the user already logged in\n\nLet me just try it - write a script, open headed Playwright, take screenshots, and if there's a QR code I'll send it for the user to scan. In fact, many Keycloak/Feishu SSO setups use QR code scanning on mobile Feishu.\n\nLet me write a pragmatic script for this.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"好，我开 headed Playwright 走飞书 SSO 登录，抓到二维码发给你扫。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_P51iYyFiKLo0Ly28MYTK4981","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"// DevOps 登录 - Playwright headed 模式，走飞书 SSO\n// 如果出现二维码则截图发送\nimport { chromium } from 'playwright';\nimport fs from 'fs';\nimport path from 'path';\nimport { fileURLToPath } from 'url';\n\nconst __filename = fileURLToPath(import.meta.url);\nconst __dirname = path.dirname(__filename);\nconst WORKSPACE_DIR = path.resolve(__dirname, '..');\nconst COOKIES_FILE = path.join(WORKSPACE_DIR, 'devops_cookies.json');\nconst PIPELINE_URL = 'https://devops.devcloud.ztgame.com/projects/yyzy/pipelines/p-f78c977835c84b71a6d58b4746cd1c4a';\nconst SCREENSHOT_DIR = path.join(WORKSPACE_DIR, 'memory');\n\nfunction log(msg) { console.log(`[DEVOP] ${msg}`); }\nfunction sleep(ms) { return new Promise(r => setTimeout(r, ms)); }\n\nasync function main() {\n  log('=== Headed DevOps Login ===');\n\n  const browser = await chromium.launch({\n    headless: false,\n    args: ['--no-sandbox', '--disable-blink-features=AutomationControlled'],\n  });\n  const ctx = await browser.newContext({\n    viewport: { width: 1280, height: 900 },\n    locale: 'zh-CN',\n    ignoreHTTPSErrors: true,\n  });\n  const page = await ctx.newPage();\n\n  // 先访问 DevOps 页面\n  log('访问 DevOps 页面...');\n  await page.goto(PIPELINE_URL, { waitUntil: 'networkidle', timeout: 30000 });\n  await sleep(3000);\n  await page.screenshot({ path: path.join(SCREENSHOT_DIR, 'devops_step1.png'), fullPage: true });\n  log(`当前 URL: ${page.url()}`);\n\n  // 检查是否跳转到登录页\n  const url = page.url();\n  if (url.includes('keycloak') || url.includes('login') || url.includes('auth')) {\n    log('跳转到 Keycloak 登录页，尝试飞书 SSO...');\n    await page.screenshot({ path: path.join(SCREENSHOT_DIR, 'devops_keycloak_login.png'), fullPage: true });\n\n    // 找飞书登录按钮\n    const feishuBtn = await page.$('button:has-text(\"飞书\"), a:has-text(\"飞书\"), span:has-text(\"飞书\"), div:has-text(\"飞书\") >> nth=0');\n    if (feishuBtn) {\n      const btnText = await feishuBtn.textContent();\n      log(`找到按钮: \"${btnText}\"`);\n      await feishuBtn.click();\n      log('点击了飞书登录按钮');\n      await sleep(5000);\n\n      // 反复截图，看是否出现二维码或跳转\n      for (let i = 0; i < 30; i++) {\n        const currentUrl = page.url();\n        log(`[第${i+1}次检查] URL: ${currentUrl}`);\n        await page.screenshot({ path: path.join(SCREENSHOT_DIR, `devops_step_${i}.png`), fullPage: true });\n\n        // 检查页面内容是否有二维码\n        const bodyText = await page.evaluate(() => document.body.innerText.substring(0, 1000));\n        const pageTitle = await page.title();\n        log(`Title: ${pageTitle}`);\n\n        if (!currentUrl.includes('keycloak') && !currentUrl.includes('login') && !currentUrl.includes('auth')) {\n          log('✅ 已跳回 DevOps！登录成功');\n          break;\n        }\n\n        if (bodyText.includes('二维码') || bodyText.includes('扫码') || bodyText.includes('QR')) {\n          log('📱 检测到二维码登录页面');\n          // 多等一会让二维码加载\n          await sleep(3000);\n          await page.screenshot({ path: path.join(SCREENSHOT_DIR, 'devops_qrcode.png'), fullPage: true });\n          log('二维码截图已保存到 memory/devops_qrcode.png');\n          break;\n        }\n\n        await sleep(2000);\n      }\n    } else {\n      log('⚠️ 未找到飞书登录按钮');\n      const allText = await page.evaluate(() => document.body.innerText);\n      log(`页面文字: ${allText.substring(0, 500)}`);\n    }\n  } else {\n    log('✅ 直接进入 DevOps 页面，Session 有效');\n  }\n\n  // 最终截图\n  await sleep(2000);\n  await page.screenshot({ path: path.join(SCREENSHOT_DIR, 'devops_final.png'), fullPage: true });\n\n  // 保存 Cookie\n  const cookies = await ctx.cookies();\n  fs.writeFileSync(COOKIES_FILE, JSON.stringify(cookies, null, 2));\n  log(`✅ 已保存 ${cookies.length} 个 Cookie`);\n\n  // 如果 URL 回到了 DevOps 页面，说明登录成功\n  if (page.url().includes('devops.devcloud') && !page.url().includes('keycloak')) {\n    log('🎉 DevOps 登录成功！');\n  }\n\n  await browser.close();\n  log('浏览器已关闭');\n}\n\nmain().catch(e => {\n  log(`ERROR: ${e.message}`);\n  process.exit(1);\n});\n","path":"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace\\scripts\\devops_headless_login.mjs"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":4780,"output":2387,"cacheRead":30208,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":37375,"cost":{"input":0.0006692,"output":0.00066836,"cacheRead":0.000845824,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.002183384}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780296179416,"responseId":"d2561d65-5535-4ff5-b76d-ed5bba8258dc"}}
