{"type":"message","id":"d8f406cc","parentId":"8ad173dc","timestamp":"2026-06-01T06:43:20.959Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Actually, the name says \"devops_headless_login\" but it's headed mode. Let me just run it. But wait - the owner is on Feishu, they can't see the browser on the server. Let me run it and take screenshots. If a QR code appears, I'll send it to the owner.\n\nBut actually, running headed mode on a server that nobody has a display for... the browser will open but nobody can see it. The screenshots will capture whatever is on the page though.\n\nLet me think about this more practically. The Playwright headed mode will open a browser window on the server (zt-c600365). If that server is running headless (no monitor), the window might not render properly, or it might use virtual display. Screenshots should still work.\n\nLet me just run it and follow the screenshots. If I can capture a QR code, I'll send it to the owner via Feishu.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_n2ftbWBmfyQf1H3QQc1n9879","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace; node scripts/devops_headless_login.mjs","timeout":180}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":172,"output":281,"cacheRead":37248,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":37701,"cost":{"input":0.000024080000000000003,"output":0.00007868,"cacheRead":0.001042944,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.001145704}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780296198082,"responseId":"5cf30308-e107-4861-a087-5fb601f95298"}}
