{"type":"message","id":"42f8bc15","parentId":"a1439978","timestamp":"2026-06-01T06:46:31.866Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The \"user data directory is already in use\" error. Chrome is already running with that user data directory. Playwright can't launch another instance with the same profile.\n\nI can try using `--remote-debugging-port` to connect to the existing Chrome instance instead. Let me check if Chrome was launched with remote debugging. Or I can use a simpler approach - ask the user to export ALL cookies for `.devcloud.ztgame.com` and `.keycloak.devcloud.ztgame.com` from their Chrome.\n\nThe user originally only sent 2 cookies. They probably used an extension and only selected those two. They need to include the Keycloak session cookies too.\n\nLet me just ask the user to export all cookies for those two domains.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"Chrome 正在运行，不能同时开。主人，更简单的办法——麻烦用 Chrome 的 Cookie 扩展（EditThisCookie 之类的）把 **`.devcloud.ztgame.com` 和 `.keycloak.devcloud.ztgame.com`** 两个域名的**所有 Cookie** 都导出来贴给我。\n\n刚才只导了 2 个（devops_return_url 和 devops_token），但 Keycloak 的 session Cookie 没带过来，所以还是跳登录页。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":1168,"output":262,"cacheRead":44160,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":45590,"cost":{"input":0.00016352,"output":0.00007336,"cacheRead":0.0012364799999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00147336}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1780296388742,"responseId":"4edcd07e-4f28-4e3c-90a5-207f6a320f1d"}}
