{"type":"message","id":"46d5531a","parentId":"c097616f","timestamp":"2026-06-01T07:07:42.683Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user says they logged in via Feishu SSO. The problem is that the Keycloak session cookie is what matters - it's stored on the Keycloak domain (keycloak.devcloud.ztgame.com), not on devcloud.ztgame.com. But the user said they only exported 2 cookies from the devcloud domain.\n\nWait - maybe the user is saying that the login they did earlier was the Feishu SSO, and the Keycloak session cookie is already in their Chrome. They need to also export cookies from `keycloak.devcloud.ztgame.com`.\n\nLet me ask more clearly.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"明白，是飞书 SSO 登的。那 Keycloak 那边应该有 session Cookie。\n\n麻烦在扩展里把 `keycloak.devcloud.ztgame.com` 域的 Cookie 也导出来一起给我~ 一般叫 `KEYCLOAK_IDENTITY` 或 `KEYCLOAK_SESSION` 之类的。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":1804,"output":202,"cacheRead":45312,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":47318,"cost":{"input":0.00025256000000000003,"output":0.00005656,"cacheRead":0.001268736,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0015778559999999999}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1780297659895,"responseId":"90348455-6a51-4e5d-bb40-8cfa6c1f5dec"}}
