{"type":"message","id":"da18b4cd","parentId":"da872eb7","timestamp":"2026-06-01T08:26:13.077Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Excellent! When we use the `devops_token` as a Cookie (not Bearer), the User API returns 200 with user data! So the cookie does work for the DevOps API - it just needs to be sent as a cookie.\n\nBut the problem is that the React frontend loads, sees no authenticated session via Keycloak, and redirects to the Keycloak login page before it can use the cookie-based API.\n\nWait - the frontend redirects to Keycloak because the initial page load goes through Keycloak. But the API endpoint `/ms/project/api/user/users` works fine with the cookie.\n\nSo here's the key insight: The DevOps app is a SPA (React) that uses Keycloak for authentication. When the page loads in the browser, Keycloak checks for a session and if not present, redirects to the login page. But the **API endpoints** accept the `devops_token` cookie directly.\n\nSo the question is: can we trigger the pipeline through the API without going through the web UI?\n\nLet me try to find the correct API endpoint for triggering the pipeline. The Pipeline API returned 404, so maybe the URL pattern is different.\n\nLet me try different API paths.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"Token 作为 Cookie 是有效的！API 能认。问题是 Keycloak 的前端中间件拦截了页面加载。那直接调 API 触发流水线试试。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_vdkDKDBsAp5IaQeo1XjS5776","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"// DevOps API - 找流水线触发接口\nimport https from 'https';\n\nconst TOKEN = 'eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiJ9.eyJleHAiOjE3ODAzODI0MDMsInVzZXJfbmFtZSI6InllemhpanVuIn0.O5U10SOnXDR2Q02ZDOxG47hV3VAv65y09yDaZ-AO-bY';\nconst BASE = 'devops.devcloud.ztgame.com';\n\nfunction fetch(path, options = {}) {\n  return new Promise((resolve, reject) => {\n    const opts = {\n      hostname: BASE,\n      port: 443,\n      path: path,\n      method: options.method || 'GET',\n      rejectUnauthorized: false,\n      headers: {\n        'Cookie': `devops_token=${TOKEN}; devops_return_url=https://devops.devcloud.ztgame.com/projects/yyzy/pipelines/p-f78c977835c84b71a6d58b4746cd1c4a`,\n        'Content-Type': 'application/json',\n        'Accept': 'application/json, text/plain, */*',\n        'User-Agent': 'Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit/537.36',\n        ...options.headers,\n      }\n    };\n    const req = https.request(opts, res => {\n      let data = '';\n      res.on('data', chunk => data += chunk);\n      res.on('end', () => {\n        let parsed;\n        try { parsed = JSON.parse(data); } catch { parsed = data.substring(0, 500); }\n        resolve({ status: res.statusCode, data: parsed });\n      });\n    });\n    req.on('error', reject);\n    if (options.body) req.write(JSON.stringify(options.body));\n    req.end();\n  });\n}\n\nasync function main() {\n  // 1. 试试不同路径\n  const paths = [\n    '/ms/project/api/pipelines/p-f78c977835c84b71a6d58b4746cd1c4a/trigger',\n    '/ms/project/api/pipelines/trigger',\n    '/ms/project/api/pipelines/p-f78c977835c84b71a6d58b4746cd1c4a',\n    '/ms/project/api/pipelines/p-f78c977835c84b71a6d58b4746cd1c4a/run',\n    '/ms/project/api/pipeline/p-f78c977835c84b71a6d58b4746cd1c4a/trigger',\n    '/ms/project/api/pipeline/trigger',\n    '/ms/pipeline/api/pipelines/trigger',\n    '/ms/project/api/pipelines',\n  ];\n\n  for (const path of paths) {\n    const result = await fetch(path);\n    console.log(`GET ${path} => ${result.status}`);\n    if (result.status === 200) {\n      const str = JSON.stringify(result.data).substring(0, 300);\n      console.log(`  Data: ${str}`);\n    }\n  }\n\n  // 2. 用 POST 试触发\n  console.log('\\n--- POST 触发尝试 ---');\n  const postPaths = [\n    '/ms/project/api/pipelines/p-f78c977835c84b71a6d58b4746cd1c4a/trigger',\n    '/ms/project/api/pipelines/trigger',\n  ];\n  const triggerBody = { dest: '1v1_test', variables: { dest: '1v1_test' } };\n\n  for (const path of postPaths) {\n    const result = await fetch(path, { method: 'POST', body: triggerBody });\n    console.log(`POST ${path} => ${result.status}`);\n    const str = JSON.stringify(result.data).substring(0, 500);\n    console.log(`  Data: ${str}`);\n  }\n}\n\nmain();\n","path":"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace\\scripts\\devops_trigger_api.mjs"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":340,"output":1234,"cacheRead":53120,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":54694,"cost":{"input":0.000047600000000000005,"output":0.00034552000000000004,"cacheRead":0.0014873599999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00188048}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780302364342,"responseId":"c285e8bd-717a-4d0a-b081-30cb080a55f8"}}
