{"type":"message","id":"2f5dd22d","parentId":"b97fcb16","timestamp":"2026-06-01T08:26:36.594Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_00_ET_zZkgqoWpIARyJWv1SX5M7017","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[DEVOP] === 拦截 Keycloak + 加载 DevOps ===\n[DEVOP] 访问流水线页面...\n[DEVOP] 当前 URL: chrome-error://chromewebdata/\n[DEVOP] 标题: \n[DEVOP] 页面文本: \n[DEVOP] ⚠️ 页面可能没渲染好，看看截图...\n[DEVOP] 找到的按钮: []"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":8654,"aggregated":"[DEVOP] === 拦截 Keycloak + 加载 DevOps ===\n[DEVOP] 访问流水线页面...\n[DEVOP] 当前 URL: chrome-error://chromewebdata/\n[DEVOP] 标题: \n[DEVOP] 页面文本: \n[DEVOP] ⚠️ 页面可能没渲染好，看看截图...\n[DEVOP] 找到的按钮: []","cwd":"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1780302396594}}
{"type":"message","id":"88f9517e","parentId":"2f5dd22d","timestamp":"2026-06-01T08:26:44.823Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Blocking the Keycloak redirect entirely caused the page to fail because it couldn't be redirected. The initial request goes to the pipeline URL, but the DevOps backend responds with a Keycloak redirect, and aborting that redirect leaves the page in an error state.\n\nLet me try a different approach. Instead of blocking the redirect, let me let it go to Keycloak, but then on the Keycloak page, I'll use the devops_token to try to complete authentication. \n\nActually, wait - let me look at this from a completely different angle. The `devops_token` is a JWT that the API recognizes. When the browser enters DevOps, it first checks with Keycloak (OIDC), and Keycloak redirects to login. But the JWT-based API is a secondary authentication mechanism.\n\nLet me try to approach this differently. Instead of trying to use the Web UI, let me try to figure out the actual API paths for the pipeline. I can load the SPA JavaScript and search for API endpoint strings.\n\nActually, let me try an even simpler approach. Since I know the API works with the cookie (the user API returned 200), let me:\n1. Load the SPA but let the Keycloak redirect happen\n2. But also intercept the redirect and from there, extract the Keycloak state/code\n3. Use the devops_token to get a Keycloak session\n\nThat's too complex. Let me try another approach entirely.\n\nLet me look at the SPA's JavaScript bundles to find the API routes.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"页面直接崩了。让我从 DevOps 的前端 JS 里挖 API 路由出来。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_ZYhMVbGwww6UtBy0grWI4417","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"// 从 DevOps SPA 中提取 API 路由\nimport https from 'https';\nimport fs from 'fs';\nimport path from 'path';\nimport { fileURLToPath } from 'url';\nimport { createInterface } from 'readline';\n\nconst __filename = fileURLToPath(import.meta.url);\nconst __dirname = path.dirname(__filename);\nconst WORKSPACE_DIR = path.resolve(__dirname, '..');\nconst TOKEN = 'eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiJ9.eyJleHAiOjE3ODAzODI0MDMsInVzZXJfbmFtZSI6InllemhpanVuIn0.O5U10SOnXDR2Q02ZDOxG47hV3VAv65y09yDaZ-AO-bY';\n\nfunction fetch(url) {\n  return new Promise((resolve, reject) => {\n    const u = new URL(url);\n    const opts = {\n      hostname: u.hostname, port: 443, path: u.pathname + u.search,\n      method: 'GET', rejectUnauthorized: false,\n      headers: { 'User-Agent': 'Mozilla/5.0' }\n    };\n    https.get(opts, res => {\n      let data = '';\n      res.on('data', chunk => data += chunk);\n      res.on('end', () => resolve(data));\n    }).on('error', reject);\n  });\n}\n\nasync function main() {\n  // 拿 index 页面，找 JS bundle 路径\n  const html = await fetch('https://devops.devcloud.ztgame.com/projects/yyzy/pipelines/p-f78c977835c84b71a6d58b4746cd1c4a');\n  const jsFiles = [...html.matchAll(/src=\"(\\/assets\\/[^\"]+\\.js)\"/g)].map(m => m[1]);\n  console.log(`找到 ${jsFiles.length} 个 JS 文件`);\n\n  // 搜索包含 pipeline API 路径的 JS\n  for (const jsPath of jsFiles) {\n    const js = await fetch(`https://devops.devcloud.ztgame.com${jsPath}`);\n    if (js.length < 100) continue;\n\n    // 搜索 API 路由模式\n    const apiPatterns = js.match(/\\/ms\\/[a-z]+\\/api\\/[^\"'`\\s]{5,80}/g);\n    if (apiPatterns && apiPatterns.length > 0) {\n      const uniquePaths = [...new Set(apiPatterns)];\n      console.log(`\\n📁 ${jsPath} (${uniquePaths.length} routes)`);\n      uniquePaths.forEach(p => {\n        if (p.includes('pipeline') || p.includes('trigger') || p.includes('build') || p.includes('deploy') || p.includes('dest')) {\n          console.log(`  🔥 ${p}`);\n        }\n      });\n    }\n  }\n}\n\nmain().catch(console.error);\n","path":"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace\\scripts\\devops_find_api.mjs"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":107,"output":1063,"cacheRead"