{"type":"message","id":"abae4bf5","parentId":"c302d55e","timestamp":"2026-06-01T08:27:21.122Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Good progress! The project list worked. I can see the project info:\n- projectId: \"yyzy\"\n- projectCode: \"yyzy\"\n- id: 47\n\nBut the script crashed on the next request. Let me fix it and also try the pipelines API.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"项目列表拿到了！`yyzy` projectId=47。让我继续探索流水线 API。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_KmxeeigffZQAxo9y247b7183","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"// DevOps API 探索 - 项目yyzy的流水线\nimport https from 'https';\n\nconst TOKEN = 'eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiJ9.eyJleHAiOjE3ODAzODI0MDMsInVzZXJfbmFtZSI6InllemhpanVuIn0.O5U10SOnXDR2Q02ZDOxG47hV3VAv65y09yDaZ-AO-bY';\n\nfunction api(path, options = {}) {\n  return new Promise((resolve, reject) => {\n    const cookie = `devops_token=${TOKEN}; devops_return_url=https://devops.devcloud.ztgame.com/projects/yyzy/pipelines/p-f78c977835c84b71a6d58b4746cd1c4a`;\n    const opts = {\n      hostname: 'devops.devcloud.ztgame.com',\n      port: 443, path,\n      method: options.method || 'GET',\n      rejectUnauthorized: false,\n      headers: { 'Cookie': cookie, 'Content-Type': 'application/json', 'Accept': 'application/json, text/plain, */*',\n        'Referer': 'https://devops.devcloud.ztgame.com/', 'User-Agent': 'Mozilla/5.0', ...options.headers }\n    };\n    const req = https.request(opts, res => {\n      let data = '';\n      res.on('data', chunk => data += chunk);\n      res.on('end', () => {\n        try { resolve({ status: res.statusCode, data: JSON.parse(data), headers: res.headers }); }\n        catch { resolve({ status: res.statusCode, data: data.substring(0, 500), headers: res.headers }); }\n      });\n    });\n    req.on('error', reject);\n    if (options.body) req.write(JSON.stringify(options.body));\n    req.end();\n  });\n}\n\nasync function main() {\n  const paths = [\n    '/ms/project/api/pipelines/list?projectId=yyzy',\n    '/ms/project/api/pipelines/list?projectCode=yyzy',\n    '/ms/project/api/pipeline/list?projectId=yyzy',\n    '/ms/project/api/pipeline/list?projectCode=yyzy',\n    '/ms/project/api/pipelines/all?projectId=yyzy',\n    '/ms/project/api/pipelines/47',\n    '/ms/project/api/pipelines?projectId=47',\n    '/ms/project/api/pipeline/my?projectCode=yyzy',\n    '/ms/project/api/pipeline/my?projectId=47',\n  ];\n\n  for (const p of paths) {\n    const r = await api(p);\n    if (r.status !== 404) {\n      const str = JSON.stringify(r.data).substring(0, 400);\n      console.log(`✅ ${p} => ${r.status}: ${str}`);\n    } else {\n      console.log(`➖ ${p} => 404`);\n    }\n  }\n}\n\nmain();\n","path":"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace\\scripts\\devops_explore_api2.mjs"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":683,"output":813,"cacheRead":62208,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":63704,"cost":{"input":0.00009562000000000001,"output":0.00022764,"cacheRead":0.0017418239999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.002065084}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780302435532,"responseId":"d61062c3-0118-43a5-b64c-aefe603fe8dd"}}
