{"type":"message","id":"0fbe3f47","parentId":"1494047a","timestamp":"2026-06-01T08:27:23.055Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_00_ET_KFJzBaaTy3OokGjc7Bbb7360","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"➖ /ms/project/api/pipelines/list?projectId=yyzy => 404\n➖ /ms/project/api/pipelines/list?projectCode=yyzy => 404\n➖ /ms/project/api/pipeline/list?projectId=yyzy => 404\n➖ /ms/project/api/pipeline/list?projectCode=yyzy => 404\n➖ /ms/project/api/pipelines/all?projectId=yyzy => 404\n➖ /ms/project/api/pipelines/47 => 404\n➖ /ms/project/api/pipelines?projectId=47 => 404\n➖ /ms/project/api/pipeline/my?projectCode=yyzy => 404\n➖ /ms/project/api/pipeline/my?projectId=47 => 404"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":295,"aggregated":"➖ /ms/project/api/pipelines/list?projectId=yyzy => 404\n➖ /ms/project/api/pipelines/list?projectCode=yyzy => 404\n➖ /ms/project/api/pipeline/list?projectId=yyzy => 404\n➖ /ms/project/api/pipeline/list?projectCode=yyzy => 404\n➖ /ms/project/api/pipelines/all?projectId=yyzy => 404\n➖ /ms/project/api/pipelines/47 => 404\n➖ /ms/project/api/pipelines?projectId=47 => 404\n➖ /ms/project/api/pipeline/my?projectCode=yyzy => 404\n➖ /ms/project/api/pipeline/my?projectId=47 => 404","cwd":"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1780302443055}}
{"type":"message","id":"7fe10dca","parentId":"0fbe3f47","timestamp":"2026-06-01T08:27:31.471Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"All 404. The pipeline API routes must be under a different base path. Let me look at the JS bundle more carefully. The routes from the project API show `/ms/project/api/` as the prefix. But maybe pipelines use a different microservice.\n\nLet me check the HTML more carefully to find the actual API base URL from the SPA config, and also look for any TypeScript/configuration that reveals the API structure.\n\nActually, let me fetch the lazy-loaded JS files that are loaded when the pipeline page renders. Those files contain the actual API calls.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_2cIC6jUke1W8zaGA0x2t8648","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"// 分析 SPA 中所有 lazy load 的 JS 路径\nimport https from 'https';\n\nfunction fetch(url) {\n  return new Promise((resolve, reject) => {\n    const u = new URL(url);\n    https.get({ hostname: u.hostname, port: 443, path: u.pathname + u.search, rejectUnauthorized: false,\n      headers: { 'User-Agent': 'Mozilla/5.0' } }, res => {\n      let data = '';\n      res.on('data', chunk => data += chunk);\n      res.on('end', () => resolve(data));\n    }).on('error', reject);\n  });\n}\n\nasync function main() {\n  // 拿主页 HTML\n  const html = await fetch('https://devops.devcloud.ztgame.com/projects/yyzy/pipelines/p-f78c977835c84b71a6d58b4746cd1c4a');\n  \n  // 拿主 JS bundle\n  const jsFiles = [...html.matchAll(/src=\"(\\/assets\\/[^\"]+\\.js)\"/g)].map(m => m[1]);\n  \n  for (const jsPath of jsFiles.filter(f => f.includes('index'))) {\n    const js = await fetch(`https://devops.devcloud.ztgame.com${jsPath}`);\n    \n    // 找所有延迟加载的模块\n    const lazyModules = [...js.matchAll(/\"([^\"]{10,150}\\.js)\"/g)];\n    const uniqueMods = [...new Set(lazyModules.map(m => m[1]))];\n    \n    console.log(`\\n📁 ${jsPath} - ${uniqueMods.length} lazy加载模块`);\n    uniqueMods.filter(f => f.includes('pipeline') || f.includes('trigger')).forEach(f => console.log(`  🔥 ${f}`));\n    \n    // 搜 API base URL\n    const baseUrls = [...js.matchAll(/['\"`](\\/ms\\/[a-z]+\\/api)['\"`]/g)];\n    [...new Set(baseUrls.map(m => m[1]))].forEach(u => console.log(`  📡 MS API: ${u}`));\n    \n    // 搜 pipeline API 相关\n    const pipelineApis = [...js.matchAll(/['\"`](\\/[^'\"`]*pipeline[^'\"`]{0,80})['\"`]/g)];\n    const uniqueApis = [...new Set(pipelineApis.map(m => m[1]))];\n    uniqueApis.forEach(a => console.log(`  📡 Pipeline API: ${a}`));\n  }\n}\n\nmain();\n","path":"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace\\scripts\\devops_lazy_load.mjs"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":282,"output":756,"cacheRead":63744,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":64782,"cost":{"input":0.00003948,"output":0.00021168,"cacheRead":0.0017848319999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.002035992}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780302443057,"responseId":"2d910fdb-84c0-4185-b4b0-533c6f354982"}}
