{"type":"message","id":"b5552bbd","parentId":"264c6801","timestamp":"2026-06-01T08:29:19.566Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now let me run the Chrome extraction script. But I need to update it to not launch as persistent context (which opens headed Chrome) - instead, I should use a standalone context that reads from the Chrome user data.\n\nWait, the `launchPersistentContext` is actually the right approach - it connects to the existing Chrome user data directory. The issue before was that Chrome was already running. Now the user should have closed it.\n\nLet me also make the script better - not opening headed mode since the user won't see it anyway, and just extracting the cookies directly.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_KAWbpHG7LHkXxGQkYXhY1910","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"// 用 Playwright 从 Chrome 用户数据目录提取 DevOps Cookie\nimport { chromium } from 'playwright';\nimport fs from 'fs';\nimport path from 'path';\nimport { fileURLToPath } from 'url';\n\nconst __filename = fileURLToPath(import.meta.url);\nconst __dirname = path.dirname(__filename);\nconst WORKSPACE_DIR = path.resolve(__dirname, '..');\nconst CHROME_PROFILE = 'C:\\\\Users\\\\yyzypublic\\\\AppData\\\\Local\\\\Google\\\\Chrome\\\\User Data';\nconst COOKIES_FILE = path.join(WORKSPACE_DIR, 'devops_cookies.json');\n\nfunction log(msg) { console.log(`[CHROME] ${msg}`); }\n\nasync function main() {\n  log('从本地 Chrome 提取 DevOps Cookie...');\n  log(`Chrome 用户数据目录: ${CHROME_PROFILE}`);\n\n  const browser = await chromium.launchPersistentContext(CHROME_PROFILE, {\n    headless: true,\n    channel: 'chrome',\n    args: ['--no-sandbox'],\n    ignoreHTTPSErrors: true,\n  });\n\n  const page = await browser.newPage();\n\n  // 访问 DevOps 流水线页面\n  log('访问 DevOps 页面...');\n  await page.goto('https://devops.devcloud.ztgame.com/projects/yyzy/pipelines/p-f78c977835c84b71a6d58b4746cd1c4a', {\n    waitUntil: 'networkidle',\n    timeout: 30000,\n  });\n\n  // 等 5 秒渲染\n  await new Promise(r => setTimeout(r, 5000));\n\n  const url = page.url();\n  const title = await page.title();\n  log(`URL: ${url}`);\n  log(`Title: ${title}`);\n\n  // 看看是否在登录页面\n  if (url.includes('keycloak') || url.includes('login')) {\n    log('⚠️ 没有登录状态，需要登录...');\n    // 截个图看看情况\n    const screenshotPath = path.join(WORKSPACE_DIR, 'memory', 'chrome_extract_state.png');\n    await page.screenshot({ path: screenshotPath });\n    log(`截图已保存: ${screenshotPath}`);\n  } else {\n    log('✅ 已有登录状态！');\n  }\n\n  // 提取全部 cookie\n  const allCookies = await browser.cookies();\n  \n  // 过滤 DevOps 相关\n  const devopsCookies = allCookies.filter(c =>\n    c.domain.includes('devcloud.ztgame.com') || c.domain.includes('keycloak')\n  );\n\n  log(`全部 Cookie: ${allCookies.length} 个`);\n  log(`DevOps 相关 Cookie: ${devopsCookies.length} 个`);\n  devopsCookies.forEach(c => log(`  ${c.domain} - ${c.name}`));\n\n  // 保存\n  fs.writeFileSync(COOKIES_FILE, JSON.stringify(devopsCookies, null, 2));\n  log(`✅ Cookie 已保存: ${COOKIES_FILE}`);\n\n  await browser.close();\n}\n\nmain().catch(e => {\n  log(`ERROR: ${e.message}`);\n  process.exit(1);\n});\n","path":"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace\\scripts\\devops_extract_chrome2.mjs"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":55,"output":893,"cacheRead":67072,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":68020,"cost":{"input":0.0000077,"output":0.00025004000000000004,"cacheRead":0.001878016,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.002135756}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780302552361,"responseId":"f17995c8-0950-49c4-ac0f-2f8efaa9894c"}}
