{"type":"message","id":"3793eebb","parentId":"e2d7849a","timestamp":"2026-06-01T08:31:11.150Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Still SIGKILL. This might be because `launchPersistentContext` requires Chrome to be freshly launched and the user data directory might have lock files still. Or there might be a crash. Let me try a different approach.\n\nActually, the issue might be that `launchPersistentContext` opens Chrome with the existing profile, but Chrome has lock files (`Parent.lock` or `SingletonLock`) that haven't been cleaned up yet even after the process was killed.\n\nLet me try:\n1. Delete the lock files first\n2. Then try again\n\nOr let me try a different approach entirely - use `chromium.launch` with `--user-data-dir` pointing to a TEMP directory, not the real Chrome profile. This would be a fresh Chrome. Then I don't need to worry about the existing Chrome profile. But then I wouldn't have the existing cookies either...\n\nActually wait, the current cookies file (`devops_cookies.json`) has 2 cookies. Let me check what Playwright wrote to it.\n\nActually no, the script didn't save anything because it crashed.\n\nLet me try yet another approach. Instead of using the Chrome user data, let me:\n1. Delete lock files from Chrome user data directory\n2. Wait a second\n3. Try the extraction again","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_CQtVVa9dV8Gyq2b3wywa9442","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# 清理 Chrome 锁文件\nRemove-Item -Path \"$env:LOCALAPPDATA\\Google\\Chrome\\User Data\\SingletonLock\" -Force -ErrorAction SilentlyContinue\nRemove-Item -Path \"$env:LOCALAPPDATA\\Google\\Chrome\\User Data\\SingletonCookie\" -Force -ErrorAction SilentlyContinue\nRemove-Item -Path \"$env:LOCALAPPDATA\\Google\\Chrome\\User Data\\SingletonSocket\" -Force -ErrorAction SilentlyContinue\nRemove-Item -Path \"$env:LOCALAPPDATA\\Google\\Chrome\\User Data\\Default\\Parent.lock\" -Force -ErrorAction SilentlyContinue\nWrite-Output \"清理完毕，等 3 秒...\"\nStart-Sleep -Seconds 3\nWrite-Output \"重试提取...\"","timeout":10}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":307,"output":498,"cacheRead":68864,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":69669,"cost":{"input":0.000042980000000000005,"output":0.00013944,"cacheRead":0.001928192,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.002110612}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780302666712,"responseId":"e65b6067-3094-46fe-bf68-8c5ce7dd723b"}}
