{"type":"message","id":"9793c71d","parentId":"60bb9d86","timestamp":"2026-06-01T08:31:58.163Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Still busy. Something else has a lock on the file. Maybe the anti-virus or the system itself. Let me try using PowerShell's Copy-Item instead, or use cmd's `copy` command.\n\nOr better yet, let me try using `fsutil` to check if the file is locked, or use Windows' `handle` tool.\n\nActually, let me try a different approach entirely. Instead of trying to copy the file, let me directly open the SQLite database from its original path. The EBUSY is from the `fs.copyFileSync` call not from SQLite.\n\nLet me modify the script to not copy the file but just open it directly (using the `PRAGMA` to handle locks).","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_PspNlkzQRiQXWtJmky2l8868","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace\\scripts\\devops_extract_sqlite.mjs","edits":[{"oldText":"  // 先复制一份（避免锁冲突）\n  const tmpPath = path.join(WORKSPACE_DIR, 'memory', 'chrome_cookies_tmp.db');\n  try { fs.unlinkSync(tmpPath); } catch {}\n  fs.copyFileSync(dbPath, tmpPath);\n  log(`已复制到临时文件`);\n\n  const db = new Database(tmpPath, { readonly: true, fileMustExist: true });","newText":"  // 用 cmd 的 copy 命令复制（避免 Node.js 的 EBUSY）\n  const tmpPath = path.join(WORKSPACE_DIR, 'memory', 'chrome_cookies_tmp.db');\n  try { fs.unlinkSync(tmpPath); } catch {}\n  const cp = require('child_process');\n  cp.execSync(`copy \"${dbPath}\" \"${tmpPath}\"`, { stdio: 'pipe' });\n  log(`已复制到临时文件`);\n\n  const db = new Database(tmpPath, { readonly: true, fileMustExist: true });\n  db.pragma('journal_mode = OFF');"}]}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":247,"output":496,"cacheRead":74496,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":75239,"cost":{"input":0.000034580000000000004,"output":0.00013888,"cacheRead":0.002085888,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.