{"type":"message","id":"d6ca8267","parentId":"570b1ba0","timestamp":"2026-06-01T08:32:19.452Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_00_y7mnHWisFozAg82KjHeT8370","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[\n  {\n    \"name\": \"devops_return_url\",\n    \"value\": \"\",\n    \"domain\": \".devcloud.ztgame.com\",\n    \"path\": \"/\",\n    \"httpOnly\": false,\n    \"secure\": false,\n    \"sameSite\": \"None\",\n    \"expires\": 13424855998\n  },\n  {\n    \"name\": \"devops_token\",\n    \"value\": \"\",\n    \"domain\": \".devcloud.ztgame.com\",\n    \"path\": \"/\",\n    \"httpOnly\": false,\n    \"secure\": false,\n    \"sameSite\": \"None\",\n    \"expires\": 13424856004\n  },\n  {\n    \"name\": \"locale\",\n    \"value\": \"\",\n    \"domain\": \".feishu-robot.devcloud.ztgame.com\",\n    \"path\": \"/\",\n    \"httpOnly\": false,\n    \"secure\": false,\n    \"sameSite\": \"None\",\n    \"expires\": 13456333448\n  },\n  {\n    \"name\": \"known_sign_in\",\n    \"value\": \"\",\n    \"domain\": \".git.devcloud.ztgame.com\",\n    \"path\": \"/\",\n    \"httpOnly\": true,\n    \"secure\": true,\n    \"sameSite\": \"None\",\n    \"expires\": 13425019465\n  },\n  {\n    \"name\": \"KEYCLOAK_SESSION\",\n    \"value\": \"\",\n    \"domain\": \".keycloak.devcloud.ztgame.com\",\n    \"path\": \"/auth/realms/giant/\",\n    \"httpOnly\": false,\n    \"secure\": true,\n    \"sameSite\": \"None\",\n    \"expires\": 13427361604\n  },\n  {\n    \"name\": \"KEYCLOAK_SESSION_LEGACY\",\n    \"value\": \"\",\n    \"domain\": \".keycloak.devcloud.ztgame.com\",\n    \"path\": \"/auth/realms/giant/\",\n    \"httpOnly\": false,\n    \"secure\": false,\n    \"sameSite\": \"None\",\n    \"expires\": 13427361604\n  }\n]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1780302739452}}
{"type":"message","id":"469791ff","parentId":"d6ca8267","timestamp":"2026-06-01T08:32:31.244Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The cookies are there but the `value` fields are all empty! This is because Chrome encrypts the cookie values in the database. The `value` column returned empty strings (or very short values) because it's stored in the `encrypted_value` column.\n\nBut wait, the SQL query selected `value` from the `cookies` table. In Chrome's cookie encryption model:\n- For cookies WITHOUT `httponly`: the value is stored in the `value` column as plaintext\n- For cookies WITH `httponly`: the value might be encrypted\n\nBut in newer Chrome (127+), all cookie values are encrypted using AES-256-GCM.\n\nWait, actually, looking at the output more carefully, the values in the DB might be empty because Chrome stores the actual encrypted values in the `encrypted_value` column (a BLOB). The `value` column in the `cookies` table might just be empty or contain metadata.\n\nLet me check the table schema to understand the column structure.\n\nActually, in Chrome's current implementation:\n- `cookies` table has columns like: `creation_utc`, `host_key`, `top_frame_site_key`, `name`, `value`, `encrypted_value`, `path`, `expires_utc`, `is_secure`, `is_httponly`, etc.\n- The `value` column stores plaintext values for most cookies\n- The `encrypted_value` column stores encrypted values for cookies requiring encryption\n\nWait but our values are empty... Let me check if the `encrypted_value` column has data. But actually the issue might be much simpler - Chrome might have re-encrypted the database after the ungraceful shutdown and the `value` column might be empty because it's stored in the encrypted_value column only now.\n\nLet me modify the script to read both columns.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"Cookie 的 value 都是空的，Chrome 新版把值加密存了，我改一下读 `encrypted_value` 列。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_TkDL30uwuaOMMI1xVg203606","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace\\scripts\\devops_extract_sqlite.mjs","edits":[{"oldText":"  const rows = db.prepare(`\n    SELECT host_key, name, value, path, is_secure, is_httponly, expires_utc, has_expires, priority, samesite\n    FROM cookies\n    WHERE host_key LIKE '%devcloud.ztgame.com%' OR host_key LIKE '%keycloak%'\n    ORDER BY host_key, name\n  `).all();\n\n  log(`找到 ${rows.length} 个相关 Cookie`);\n  \n  // 调试信息：列出所有找到的\n  rows.forEach(r => log(`  ${r.host_key} - ${r.name}: ${r.value.substring(0, 40)}...`));","newText":"  // 先探测表结构\n  const columns = db.prepare(`PRAGMA table_info(cookies)`).all();\n  log('表字段:', columns.map(c => c.name).join(', '));\n  const hasEncrypted = columns.some(c => c.name === 'encrypted_value');\n\n  const rows = db.prepare(`\n    SELECT host_key, name, value${hasEncrypted ? ', encrypted_value' : ''}, path, is_secure, is_httponly, expires_utc, has_expires, priority, samesite\n    FROM cookies\n    WHERE host_key LIKE '%devcloud.ztgame.com%' OR host_key LIKE '%keycloak%'\n    ORDER BY host_key, name\n  `).all();\n\n  log(`找到 ${rows.length} 个相关 Cookie`);\n  \n  // 调试信息\n  rows.forEach(r => {\n    const val = r.value || '';\n    const encLen = r.encrypted_value ? r.encrypted_value.length : 0;\n    log(`  ${r.host_key} - ${r.name}: value='${val.substring(0, 30)}' enc_len=${encLen}`);\n  });"},{"oldText":"  // 转换为 Playwright 格式\n  const cookies = rows.map(r => {\n    // 处理 domain - Chrome 可能存的是 .devcloud.ztgame.com 或 devcloud.ztgame.com\n    let domain = r.host_key;\n    if (!domain.startsWith('.')) domain = '.' + domain;\n\n    // 转换过期时间（Chrome 是微秒，Playwright 是秒）\n    let expires = r.has_expires ? Math.floor(r.expires_utc / 1000000) : Date.now()/1000 + 86400;\n\n    return {\n      name: r.name,\n      value: r.value,\n      domain: domain,\n      path: r.path || '/',\n      httpOnly: !!r.is_httponly,\n      secure: !!r.is_secure,\n      sameSite: ['None', 'Lax', 'Strict'][r.samesite] || 'None',\n      expires: Math.max(expires, Date.now()/1000 + 3600), // 至少 1 小时后过期\n    };\n  });","newText":"  // 转换为 Playwright 格式\n  const cookies = rows.map(r => {\n    let domain = r.host_key;\n    if (!domain.startsWith('.')) domain = '.' + domain;\n    let expires = r.has_expires ? Math.floor(r.expires_utc / 1000000) : Date.now()/1000 + 86400;\n\n    // 如果 value 为空但有 encrypted_value，尝试解密\n    let value = r.value;\n    if ((!value || value === '') && r.encrypted_value && r.encrypted_value.length > 0) {\n      log(`⚠️ ${r.name}: value 为空，encrypted_value 长度=${r.encrypted_value.length}，需要 DPAPI 解密`);\n      // 保持空值，后续需用其他方法\n    }\n\n    return {\n      name: r.name,\n      value: value || '',\n      domain: domain,\n      path: r.path || '/',\n      httpOnly: !!r.is_httponly,\n      secure: !!r.is_secure,\n      sameSite: ['None', 'Lax', 'Strict'][r.samesite] || 'None',\n      expires: Math.max(expires, Date.now()/1000 + 3600),\n    };\n  });"}]}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":553,"output":1498,"cacheRead":77440,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":79491,"cost":{"input":0.00007742,"output":0.00041944000000000004,"cacheRead":0.00216832,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00266518}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780302739455,"responseId":"3eb6d724-3b9e-4708-a8b2-39738a69ed54"}}
