{"type":"message","id":"47846208","parentId":"c1f04f48","timestamp":"2026-06-01T08:34:51.796Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I found it! The axios client creation:\n\n```javascript\nconst t = ie.create({baseURL: e === \"devops\" ? \"/ms\" : \"/\", withCredentials: true});\n```\n\nSo when the API type is \"devops\", the base URL is `/ms`. Looking at the pipelines module, the API client `a` is imported from `./index-C6ONAmdr.js` as `C`. And then the API functions use paths like `\"process/api/user/builds/...\"`. So the full URL path would be:\n\n**`/ms/process/api/user/builds/{projectCode}/{pipelineId}`**\n\nLet me try this!\n\nThe manual startup pipeline function:\n- `v` (getManualStartupInfo): `a.get(\"process/api/user/builds/\".concat(e,\"/\").concat(t,\"/manualStartupInfo\"))`\n  → GET `/ms/process/api/user/builds/yyzy/p-f78c977835c84b71a6d58b4746cd1c4a/manualStartupInfo`\n\n- `R` (manualStartupPipeline): `a.post(\"process/api/user/builds/\".concat(e,\"/\").concat(t))`\n  → POST `/ms/process/api/user/builds/yyzy/p-f78c977835c84b71a6d58b4746cd1c4a`\n  with body containing variables\n\nLet me try the POST directly!","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"找到了！baseURL 是 `/ms`，API 路径是 `/ms/process/api/user/builds/{projectCode}/{pipelineId}`。试试直接触发流水线！"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_lhtrR78qsTqrUX59Bbra2402","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"// 触发 DevOps 流水线！直接调 API\nimport https from 'https';\n\nconst TOKEN = 'eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiJ9.eyJleHAiOjE3ODAzODI0MDMsInVzZXJfbmFtZSI6InllemhpanVuIn0.O5U10SOnXDR2Q02ZDOxG47hV3VAv65y09yDaZ-AO-bY';\nconst COOKIE = `devops_token=${TOKEN}; devops_return_url=https://devops.devcloud.ztgame.com/projects/yyzy/pipelines/p-f78c977835c84b71a6d58b4746cd1c4a`;\nconst BASE = 'devops.devcloud.ztgame.com';\n\nfunction api(method, path, body) {\n  return new Promise(resolve => {\n    const opts = {\n      hostname: BASE, port: 443, path,\n      method, rejectUnauthorized: false,\n      headers: {\n        'Cookie': COOKIE, 'Content-Type': 'application/json',\n        'Accept': 'application/json, text/plain, */*',\n        'Referer': 'https://devops.devcloud.ztgame.com/projects/yyzy/pipelines/p-f78c977835c84b71a6d58b4746cd1c4a',\n        'User-Agent': 'Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit/537.36',\n        'X-Requested-With': 'XMLHttpRequest',\n      }\n    };\n    const req = https.request(opts, res => {\n      let data = '';\n      res.on('data', chunk => data += chunk);\n      res.on('end', () => {\n        let parsed;\n        try { parsed = JSON.parse(data); } catch { parsed = data.substring(0, 500); }\n        console.log(`${method} ${path} => ${res.statusCode}`);\n        console.log(`  Response: ${JSON.stringify(parsed).substring(0, 500)}`);\n        resolve({ status: res.statusCode, data: parsed });\n      });\n    });\n    req.on('error', e => resolve({ status: -1, data: e.message }));\n    if (body) req.write(JSON.stringify(body));\n    req.end();\n  });\n}\n\nasync function main() {\n  const projectCode = 'yyzy';\n  const pipelineId = 'p-f78c977835c84b71a6d58b4746cd1c4a';\n\n  // 1. Test the base path for the DevOps API\n  console.log('=== 测试 API 路径 ===');\n  const r = await api('GET', `/ms/process/api/user/builds/${projectCode}/${pipelineId}/manualStartupInfo`);\n  console.log('');\n\n  // 2. Also test the user API to confirm cookie is still valid\n  console.log('=== 确认 Cookie 有效 ===');\n  const r2 = await api('GET', '/ms/project/api/user/users');\n  console.log('');\n\n  // 3. Try to trigger the pipeline\n  console.log('=== 触发流水线 ===');\n  const triggerResult = await api('POST', `/ms/process/api/user/builds/${projectCode}/${pipelineId}`, {\n    dest: '1v1_test'\n  });\n}\n\nmain();\n","path":"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace\\scripts\\devops_trigger_v2.mjs"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":719,"output":1154,"cacheRead":98944,"cacheWri