{"type":"message","id":"2d5c2e0a","parentId":"f972d8ee","timestamp":"2026-06-01T08:34:57.348Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_00_6sAwA2gWrzve5MA686v41695","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"=== 测试 API 路径 ===\nGET /ms/process/api/user/builds/yyzy/p-f78c977835c84b71a6d58b4746cd1c4a/manualStartupInfo => 200\n  Response: {\"status\":0,\"data\":{\"canManualStartup\":true,\"canElementSkip\":false,\"properties\":[{\"id\":\"dest\",\"required\":false,\"type\":\"ENUM\",\"defaultValue\":\"1v1_qa\",\"options\":[{\"key\":\"1v1_test\",\"value\":\"1v1_test\"},{\"key\":\"1v1_dev\",\"value\":\"1v1_dev\"},{\"key\":\"1v1_zhuanxiang\",\"value\":\"1v1_zhuanxiang\"},{\"key\":\"1v1_qa\",\"value\":\"1v1_qa\"},{\"key\":\"1v1_cehua1\",\"value\":\"1v1_cehua1\"},{\"key\":\"1v1_cehua2\",\"value\":\"1v1_cehua2\"}],\"desc\":\"目标目录\",\"key\":\"818e65af-6d02-40d7-8542-b969afc08937\",\"displayConfig\":\"DISPLAY_AND_REQUIRED\"\n\n=== 确认 Cookie 有效 ===\nGET /ms/project/api/user/users => 200\n  Response: {\"code\":0,\"data\":{\"chineseName\":\"叶枝君\",\"avatarUrl\":\"\",\"username\":\"yezhijun\",\"department\":\"月圆之夜/月圆之夜项目组\",\"mail\":\"yezhijun@ztgame.com\",\"title\":\"CCG客户端主程\",\"permissions\":[],\"net\":\"OFFICE\"}}\n\n=== 触发流水线 ===\nPOST /ms/process/api/user/builds/yyzy/p-f78c977835c84b71a6d58b4746cd1c4a => 200\n  Response: {\"status\":0,\"data\":{\"id\":\"b-a255c944da30422db318075c604f28d8\"}}"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":562,"aggregated":"=== 测试 API 路径 ===\nGET /ms/process/api/user/builds/yyzy/p-f78c977835c84b71a6d58b4746cd1c4a/manualStartupInfo => 200\n  Response: {\"status\":0,\"data\":{\"canManualStartup\":true,\"canElementSkip\":false,\"properties\":[{\"id\":\"dest\",\"required\":false,\"type\":\"ENUM\",\"defaultValue\":\"1v1_qa\",\"options\":[{\"key\":\"1v1_test\",\"value\":\"1v1_test\"},{\"key\":\"1v1_dev\",\"value\":\"1v1_dev\"},{\"key\":\"1v1_zhuanxiang\",\"value\":\"1v1_zhuanxiang\"},{\"key\":\"1v1_qa\",\"value\":\"1v1_qa\"},{\"key\":\"1v1_cehua1\",\"value\":\"1v1_cehua1\"},{\"key\":\"1v1_cehua2\",\"value\":\"1v1_cehua2\"}],\"desc\":\"目标目录\",\"key\":\"818e65af-6d02-40d7-8542-b969afc08937\",\"displayConfig\":\"DISPLAY_AND_REQUIRED\"\n\n=== 确认 Cookie 有效 ===\nGET /ms/project/api/user/users => 200\n  Response: {\"code\":0,\"data\":{\"chineseName\":\"叶枝君\",\"avatarUrl\":\"\",\"username\":\"yezhijun\",\"department\":\"月圆之夜/月圆之夜项目组\",\"mail\":\"yezhijun@ztgame.com\",\"title\":\"CCG客户端主程\",\"permissions\":[],\"net\":\"OFFICE\"}}\n\n=== 触发流水线 ===\nPOST /ms/process/api/user/builds/yyzy/p-f78c977835c84b71a6d58b4746cd1c4a => 200\n  Response: {\"status\":0,\"data\":{\"id\":\"b-a255c944da30422db318075c604f28d8\"}}","cwd":"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1780302897347}}
{"type":"message","id":"1cd3272a","parentId":"2d5c2e0a","timestamp":"2026-06-01T08:35:06.661Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"EXCELLENT! 🎉🎉🎉\n\nThe API works perfectly!\n\n1. **GET manualStartupInfo** - Returns the available parameters for this pipeline:\n   - `dest` parameter: `type: \"ENUM\"`, options include `1v1_test`, `1v1_dev`, `1v1_zhuanxiang`, `1v1_qa`, `1v1_cehua1`, `1v1_cehua2`\n   - Default: `1v1_qa`\n   - `canManualStartup: true` - We can trigger!\n\n2. **POST to trigger** - SUCCESS! \n   - Response: `{\"id\":\"b-a255c944da30422db318075c604f28d8\"}`\n   - This is the build ID! The pipeline is running!\n\nNow I need to:\n1. Monitor the build status (poll for completion)\n2. Wait until it's done\n3. Notify the user\n\nLet me also update the keepalive state since the cookie works.\n\nLet me check the build status API from the earlier module analysis. The function `_` exported as `Z` fetches build history:\n```javascript\nconst n = \"process/api/user/builds/\".concat(e,\"/\").concat(t,\"/history/new?\").concat(c(s));\nreturn await a.get(n)\n```\n\nAnd `z` exported as `n` fetches build detail:\n```javascript\nawait a.get(\"process/api/user/builds/\".concat(e,\"/\").concat(t,\"/\").concat(s,\"/detail\"))\n```\n\nWhere e=projectCode, t=pipelineId, s=buildId.\n\nLet me poll the build detail to check status.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"## ✅ 流水线触发成功！\n\nAPI 完美找到了！流水线已启动，Build ID: `b-a255c944da30422db318075c604f28d8`。\n\n现在我轮询等它完成~"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_jvjVC3A1xthf2JhdcMja3858","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"// 监控流水线构建状态\nimport https from 'https';\nimport { setTimeout as sleep } from 'timers/promises';\n\nconst TOKEN = 'eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiJ9.eyJleHAiOjE3ODAzODI0MDMsInVzZXJfbmFtZSI6InllemhpanVuIn0.O5U10SOnXDR2Q02ZDOxG47hV3VAv65y09yDaZ-AO-bY';\nconst COOKIE = `devops_token=${TOKEN}; devops_return_url=https://devops.devcloud.ztgame.com/projects/yyzy/pipelines/p-f78c977835c84b71a6d58b4746cd1c4a`;\nconst BASE = 'devops.devcloud.ztgame.com';\nconst PROJECT = 'yyzy';\nconst PIPELINE = 'p-f78c977835c84b71a6d58b4746cd1c4a';\nconst BUILD = 'b-a255c944da30422db318075c604f28d8';\n\nfunction api(method, path, body) {\n  return new Promise(resolve => {\n    const opts = {\n      hostname: BASE, port: 443, path, method, rejectUnauthorized: false,\n      headers: { 'Cookie': COOKIE, 'Content-Type': 'application/json',\n        'Accept': 'application/json, text/plain, */*', 'User-Agent': 'Mozilla/5.0' }\n    };\n    const req = https.request(opts, res => {\n      let data = '';\n      res.on('data', chunk => data += chunk);\n      res.on('end', () => {\n        try { resolve({ status: res.statusCode, data: JSON.parse(data) }); }\n        catch { resolve({ status: res.statusCode, data: { raw: data.substring(0, 300) } }); }\n      });\n    });\n    req.on('error', e => resolve({ status: -1, data: e.message }));\n    if (body) req.write(JSON.stringify(body));\n    req.end();\n  });\n}\n\nasync function main() {\n  console.log('开始监控构建状态...');\n  const startTime = Date.now();\n  const timeout = 10 * 60 * 1000; // 10 分钟\n\n  for (let i = 0; i < 120; i++) {\n    await sleep(5000); // 每 5 秒查一次\n    \n    const r = await api('GET', `/ms/process/api/user/builds/${PROJECT}/${PIPELINE}/${BUILD}/detail`);\n    const elapsed = Math.floor((Date.now() - startTime) / 1000);\n    \n    if (r.status !== 200 || r.data.status === undefined) {\n      console.log(`[${elapsed}s] 响应异常: ${JSON.stringify(r.data).substring(0, 100)}`);\n      continue;\n    }\n\n    const status = r.data.status;\n    const statusText = {\n      0: '待执行', 1: '排队中', 2: '运行中', 3: '成功', \n      4: '失败', 5: '已取消', 6: '已终止', 7: '部分成功'\n    }[status] || `未知(${status})`;\n\n    console.log(`[${elapsed}s] 构建状态: ${statusText} (${status})`);\n\n    if (status === 3) {\n      console.log('\\n✅ 构建成功！');\n      break;\n    } else if (status >= 4) {\n      console.log(`\\n❌ 构建完成 - 状态: ${statusText}`);\n      break;\n    }\n\n    if (Date.now() - startTime > timeout) {\n      console.log('\\n⏰ 监控超时');\n      break;\n    }\n  }\n}\n\nmain();\n","path":"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace\\scripts\\devops_monitor.mjs"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":510,"output":1330,"cacheRead":101248,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":103088,"cost":{"input":0.0000714,"output":0.0003724,"cacheRead":0.002834944,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0032787439999999997}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780302897351,"responseId":"af648eda-039c-4903-8d8a-8fd1e0773c2d"}}
