e\n  行2: A2=##type | B2=int | C2=int | D2=string\n  行3: A3=##group | B3=c,s | C3=c,s | D3=c,s\n  行4: A4=## | B4=金卡id | C4=这是card表映射id | D4=名字\n  行5: B5=101010001 | C5=1010001 | D5=恶魔公主黑天鹅\n  行6: B6=101010002 | C6=1010002 | D6=吸血鬼领主\n  行7: B7=101010003 | C7=1010003 | D7=毒蛇女王\n  行8: B8=101010004 | C8=1010004 | D8=传教士\n\n===== CardSkin.xlsx =====\n单元格范围: A1:AB51\n  行1: A1=##var | B1=id | C1=type | D1=name | E1=down_desc | F1=icon | G1=icon_bg | H1=chessIcon | I1=chessIcon_bg | J1=cardPool | K1=entrance_effect | L1=attack_effect | M1=voice_in | N1=voice_dead | O1=replacePlayEffect | S1=spine | T1=posX1 | U1=posY1 | V1=scale1 | W1=posX2 | X1=posY2 | Y1=scale2 | Z1=posX3 | AA1=posY3 | AB1=scale3\n  行2: A2=##type | B2=int | C2=int | D2=string | E2=string | F2=string | G2=string | H2=string | I2=string | J2=(list#sep=,),int | K2=string | L2=string | M2=int | N2=int | O2=map,int,int | S2=string | T2=int | U2=int | V2=float | W2=float | X2=float | Y2=float | Z2=float | AA2=float | AB2=float\n  行3: A3=##group | B3=c,s | C3=c,s | D3=c,s | E3=c | F3=c | G3=c | H3=c | I3=c | J3=c,s | K3=c | L3=c | M3=c | N3=c | O3=c,s | S3=c | T3=c | U3=c | V3=c | W3=c | X3=c | Y3=c | Z3=c | AA3=c | AB3=c\n  行4: A4=## | B4=这是id | C4=映射卡牌 | D4=名字 | E4=卡牌备注 | F4=图标 | G4=图标底图 | H4=棋子图标 | I4=棋子底图 | J4=所属牌池 | K4=入场特效相关 | L4=攻击特效相关 | M4=入场语音 | N4=死亡语音 | O4=buffid | P4=替换后的特效 | Q4=buffid | R4=替换后的特效 | S4=Spine名字 | T4=局外卡牌SpineX坐标 | U4=局外卡牌SpineY坐标 | V4=局外卡牌Spine缩放 | W4=局内卡牌SpineX坐标 | X4=局内卡牌SpineY坐标 | Y4=局内卡牌Spine缩放 | Z4=战场棋子SpineX坐标 | AA4=战场棋子SpineY坐标 | AB4=战场棋子Spine缩放\n  行5: A5=##var\n  行6: B6=510500011 | C6=1050001 | D6=疯狂科学家 | E6=出现于【旅途的开始】牌包 | F6=y01_fengkuangkexuejia | G6=y01_fengkuangkexuejia_bg | H6=y01_fengkuangkexuejia_s | I6=y01_fengkuangkexuejia_s_bg | J6=1 | K6=Fx_Solo000_Born_Mech\n  行7: B7=510600011 | C7=1060001 | D7=龙葵 | E7=出现于【旅途的开始】牌包 | F7=y01_longkui | G7=y01_longkui_bg | H7=y01_longkui_s | I7=y01_longkui_s_bg | J7=1 | K7=Fx_Solo000_Born_Natural\n  行8: B8=510400041 | C8=1040004 | D8=白眼青龙 | E8=【异画自选包01】获取 | F8=y01_baiyanqinglong | G8=y01_baiyanqinglong_bg | H8=y01_baiyanqinglong_s | I8=y01_baiyanqinglong_s_bg | J8=20001 | K8=Fx_Solo000_Born_fire","cwd":"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1780303257197}}
{"type":"message","id":"c016b90b","parentId":"2f22f596","timestamp":"2026-06-01T08:41:17.062Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I can see the structure clearly:\n\n**Card.xlsx:**\n- Row 1: Header names (##var line)\n- Row 2: Types (##type line)\n- Row 3: Groups (##group line)\n- Row 4: Descriptions (## line)\n- Row 5+: Actual data\n- Column B = `id` (Card ID)\n- Column C = `type`\n- Column D = `name`\n\n**CardGold.xlsx:**\n- Row 1: Header names\n- Row 2: Types\n- Row 3: Groups\n- Row 4: Descriptions\n- Row 5+: Actual data\n- Column B = `id` (CardGold's own ID)\n- Column C = `card_id` (Card reference!)\n- Column D = `name`\n\n**CardSkin.xlsx:**\n- Row 1: Header names\n- Row 2: Types\n- Row 3: Groups\n- Row 4: Descriptions\n- Row 5+: Actual data (with Row 5 being ##var maybe empty)\n- Column B = `id` (CardSkin's own ID)\n- Column C = `type` (mapping card type - this is the Card reference!)\n- Column D = `name`\n- Column J = `cardPool` (card pool reference, NOT Card reference)\n\nSo the correct checks are:\n1. **CardGold.card_id** → should exist in **Card.id**\n2. **CardSkin.type** (not cardPool!) → should exist in **Card.id**\n\nThe issue with my original script was:\n1. Card table reading: The `Id` column was `B` column, and sheet_to_json with `defval: null` was reading row data\n2. The `.id` field was the column header but in the data rows it should be `id`. Let me check...\n3. CardSkin check: I was checking `cardPool` column instead of `type` column\n\nThe actual data starts from row 5 in all files (rows 1-4 are metadata). But `XLSX.utils.sheet_to_json` with default options treats the first row as headers. So for Card.xlsx, the header would be the `##var` row with column names, but for CardGold and CardSkin it's similar.\n\nWait - the issue is that `sheet_to_json` uses the first row as headers. The first row in all these files is `##var`, which means the column headers are literally the `##var` row values. But then row 2 is `##type`, row 3 is `##group`, row 4 is `##` descriptions, and actual data starts from row 5.\n\nSo when I do `XLSX.utils.sheet_to_json(sheet)`, the first row (`##var`, `id`, `type`, etc.) becomes the keys. Then rows 2-4 also become objects with those same keys but with values like `##type`, `int`, etc. This is why checking `CardGold[0]` showed headers correctly.\n\nNow, for Card.xlsx with `Id` column: the first row key would be `##var`, and the actual id column header is `id` (not `Id`). So when checking `row['Id']`, it would be undefined for all rows.\n\nLet me rewrite the script properly.\n\nFor CardGold, the actual card reference is `card_id` column. Let me check if \"1010001\" etc. exist in Card's `id` column.\n\nLet me look at Card rows:\nRow 5: B5=1010001\nRow 6: B6=1010002\netc.\n\nAnd CardGold:\nRow 5: B5=101010001 (its own id), C5=1010001 (card_id reference)\n\nSo the CardGold's card_id \"1010001\" should match Card's id \"1010001\". This should work!\n\nLet me rewrite the script to:\n1. Skip rows 2-4 (metadata rows) when reading\n2. Use `card_id` column for CardGold\n3. Use `type` column for CardSkin\n4. Also look at CardSkin to see if `type` is actually a Card reference","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"看到结构了！Card 的 ID 在 `id` 列（B列），CardGold 的 `card_id` 才是 Card 引用，CardSkin 的 `type`（C列）才是映射卡牌。让我重写检查逻辑。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_GMac3PQVzOMwoJQAeMuV5680","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"// 精确检查 Excel 数据表引用完整性\nimport XLSX from 'xlsx';\nimport path from 'path';\n\nconst DATAS_DIR = 'E:\\\\Solo\\\\nightoffullmoon\\\\client\\\\config\\\\SoloConfig\\\\Datas';\n\nfunction readDataRows(fileName, headerRow = 1) {\n  const fp = path.join(DATAS_DIR, fileName);\n  const wb = XLSX.readFile(fp, { cellDates: false, raw: true });\n  const sheet = wb.Sheets[wb.SheetNames[0]];\n  \n  // 用 headerRow 作为列名行（Luban 第一行是 ##var 即列名）\n  const data = XLSX.utils.sheet_to_json(sheet, { \n    header: 1, // 按数组读取\n    defval: null,\n    raw: true,\n  });\n  \n  // 第0行（excel 行1）：列名\n  const headers = data[0] || [];\n  // 第1-3行（excel 行2-4）：类型/组/描述，跳过\n  // 第4+行（excel 行5+）：实际数据\n  const rows = data.slice(4).filter(r => r.some(c => c !== null && c !== '' && c !== undefined));\n  \n  // 转成对象数组\n  return rows.map(row => {\n    const obj = {};\n    headers.forEach((h, i) => {\n      if (h && h !== '##var' && h !== '##' && h !== '##type' && h !== '##group') {\n        obj[h] = row[i] !== undefined ? row[i] : null;\n      }\n    });\n    return obj;\n  });\n}\n\nfunction main() {\n  // 1. Card 表 - 获取所有有效 id\n  const cardData = readDataRows('Card.xlsx');\n  const cardIds = new Set(cardData.map(r => String(r['id']).trim()).filter(id => id && id !== '' && id !== 'null'));\n  \n  console.log(`📊 Card 表: ${cardData.length} 行数据, ${cardIds.size} 个有效 Id`);\n  console.log(`   Card ID 样例: ${[...cardIds].slice(0, 5).join(', ')}...`);\n\n  // 2. CardGold 表\n  const goldData = readDataRows('CardGold.xlsx');\n  console.log(`\\n📊 CardGold 表: ${goldData.length} 行数据`);\n  console.log(`   列: ${Object.keys(goldData[0] || {}).join(', ')}`);\n  \n  const goldErrors = [];\n  const goldIdSet = new Set();\n  \n  for (const row of goldData) {\n    const goldId = String(row['id'] || '').trim();\n    const cardId = String(row['card_id'] || '').trim();\n    \n    goldIdSet.add(goldId);\n    \n    if (!cardId || cardId === '' || cardId === 'null') {\n      goldErrors.push({ id: goldId, desc: `card_id 为空` });\n    } else if (!cardIds.has(cardId)) {\n      goldErrors.push({ id: goldId, card_id: cardId, name: row['name'], desc: `card_id=${cardId} 在 Card 表中不存在` });\n    }\n  }\n\n  if (goldErrors.length === 0) {\n    console.log(`✅ CardGold: 全部 ${goldData.length} 条数据的 card_id 均有效`);\n  } else {\n    console.log(`\\n❌ CardGold 发现 ${goldErrors.length} 个问题:`);\n    goldErrors.forEach((e, i) => {\n      if (i < 30) console.log(`   [${e.id}] ${e.desc}`);\n    });\n    if (goldErrors.length > 30) console.log(`   ... 还有 ${goldErrors.length - 30} 个`);\n  }\n\n  // 3. CardSkin 表\n  const skinData = readDataRows('CardSkin.xlsx');\n  console.log(`\\n📊 CardSkin 表: ${skinData.length} 行数据`);\n  console.log(`   列: ${Object.keys(skinData[0] || {}).join(', ')}`);\n\n  const skinErrors = [];\n  for (const row of skinData) {\n    const skinId = String(row['id'] || '').trim();\n    const cardRef = String(row['type'] || '').trim(); // type 列是映射卡牌\n    \n    if (!cardRef || cardRef === '' || cardRef === 'null') {\n      skinErrors.push({ id: skinId, type: cardRef, desc: `type（映射卡牌）为空` });\n    } else if (!cardIds.has(cardRef)) {\n      skinErrors.push({ id: skinId, type: cardRef, name: row['name'], desc: `type=${cardRef} 在 Card 表中不存在` });\n    }\n  }\n\n  if (skinErrors.length === 0) {\n    console.log(`✅ CardSkin: 全部 ${skinData.length} 条数据的 type（映射卡牌）均有效`);\n  } else {\n    console.log(`\\n❌ CardSkin 发现 ${skinErrors.length} 个问题:`);\n    skinErrors.forEach((e, i) => {\n      if (i < 20) console.log(`   [${e.id}] ${e.desc}`);\n    });\n    if (skinErrors.length > 20) console.log(`   ... 还有 ${skinErrors.length - 20} 个`);\n  }\n\n  // 4. 检查有无 Card 表中存在但 CardGold 中没引用的 id（孤儿检测）\n  const goldCardIds = new Set(goldData.map(r => String(r['card_id'] || '').trim()).filter(v => v));\n  const orphanedCards = [...cardIds].filter(id => !goldCardIds.has(id));\n  \n  console.log(`\\n📊 Card 中有 ${cardIds.size} 个 Id, CardGold 引用了 ${goldCardIds.size} 个`);\n  \n  // 显示前几个无金卡的 Card\n  if (orphanedCards.length > 0) {\n    console.log(`📌 ${orphanedCards.length} 个 Card 在 CardGold 中无对应金卡:`);\n    const sample = orphanedCards.slice(0, 15);\n    const cardNames = {};\n    cardData.forEach(r => { cardNames[String(r['id'])] = r['name']; });\n    sample.forEach(id => console.log(`   ${id} - ${cardNames[id] || 'unknown'}`));\n    if (orphanedCards.length > 15) console.log(`   ... 还有 ${orphanedCards.length - 15} 个`);\n  } else {\n    console.log(`✅ 所有 Card 在 CardGold 中都有对应金卡`);\n  }\n\n  // 总结\n  console.log(`\\n========================================`);\n  console.log(`📊 检查总结:`);\n  console.log(`   Card 表: ${cardData.length} 条`);\n  console.log(`   CardGold 表: ${goldData.length} 条, 引用错误: ${goldErrors.length}`);\n  console.log(`   CardSkin 表: ${skinData.length} 条, 引用错误: ${skinErrors.length}`);\n  console.log(`   Card 无金卡: ${orphanedCards.length}`);\n}\n\nmain();\n","path":"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace\\scripts\\check_card_refs_fixed.mjs"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":2734,"output":2640,"cacheRead":127872,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":133246,"cost":{"input":0.00038276,"output":0.0007392000000000001,"cacheRead":0.003580416,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.004702375999999999}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780303257199,"responseId":"514d1428-a93a-4a3a-9cb3-726a6b823ed9"}}
