{"type":"message","id":"dfcca98d","parentId":"db722bd8","timestamp":"2026-06-01T08:41:54.785Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Interesting! The encoding is a bit garbled (Chinese characters), but I can see the data clearly:\n\n1. CardGold `card_id=2000097` -> Card `id=2000097` exists! These are the main Card ID. The `200009701` entries are the buff IDs listed in the `buff` column of Card, not separate card IDs.\n\n2. `不在 Card 中的 gold card_id: []` (empty array) - confirms ALL CardGold card_id references are valid!\n\nSo my earlier concern about trailing digits was wrong - Card ID 2000097 exists, and 200009701 is a buff reference, not a separate card ID.\n\nNow let me reconsider the \"56 Card 无金卡\" report:\nThese are card IDs that have NO corresponding entry in CardGold. For example, `2000097` IS in CardGold (we just verified), but `200009702` etc. are buff entries referenced from the `buff` column, not separate Card entries.\n\nWait, but looking at the Card data again:\n- `id=2000097` - this IS a Card\n- `id=200009701` - this is also a Card row (showing id=200009701 in the debug output)\n\nLet me look at whether both `2000097` and `200009701` are in cardIds...\n\nActually from the earlier debug output:\n```\nCard 中 2000097 相关: [\n  {\"id\":2000097,...},\n  {\"id\":\"200009701\",...}\n]\n```\n\nSo both are in Card. But CardGold only references `2000097`, not `200009701`. That's fine - `200009701` might be a separate entry in Card that doesn't need a gold version.\n\nHmm, but actually looking at the buff column: `\"buff\":\"200009701,200009702\"` - this suggests 200009701 and 200009702 are buff IDs appended to the card ID 2000097, creating separate Card rows for different buff variants of the same card.\n\nMy current conclusion seems correct:\n- **CardGold**: ✅ 全部 515 条 card_id 引用有效\n- **CardSkin**: ⚠️ 1 条 type 为空（映射卡牌列未填）\n- **Card 无金卡 56 个**: 这不太算数据错误，因为不是所有卡都需要金卡版本\n\nLet me also check the CardSkin empty type issue more carefully.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"数据清楚了！其实 CardGold 全部有效，之前那 56 个\"无金卡\"的多半是 buff 变体卡。让我看看 CardSkin 那个空的 type 到底是谁，以及补金卡的情况。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_DuwlrlIdQ5ZMvj2agnmN9349","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace; node -e \"\nimport XLSX from 'xlsx';\nimport path from 'path';\n\nconst DATAS_DIR = 'E:\\\\Solo\\\\nightoffullmoon\\\\client\\\\config\\\\SoloConfig\\\\Datas';\n\nfunction readAll(fileName) {\n  const fp = path.join(DATAS_DIR, fileName);\n  const wb = XLSX.readFile(fp, { cellDates: false, raw: true });\n  const sheet = wb.Sheets[wb.SheetNames[0]];\n  const data = XLSX.utils.sheet_to_json(sheet, { header: 1, defval: null, raw: true });\n  const headers = data[0];\n  const rows = data.slice(4).filter(r => r.some(c => c !== null && c !== ''));\n  return rows.map(row => {\n    const obj = {};\n    headers.forEach((h, i) => { if (h && h !== '##var') obj[h] = row[i]; });\n    return obj;\n  });\n}\n\nconst skin = readAll('CardSkin.xlsx');\nconsole.log('=== CardSkin 中 type 为空的记录 ===');\nskin.filter(r => !r.type).forEach(r => console.log(JSON.stringify(r)));\n\n// 找出 CardGold 没有但 Card 有的 id（可能是需要补金卡的）\nconst gold = readAll('CardGold.xlsx');\nconst card = readAll('Card.xlsx');\n\nconst cardIds = new Set(card.map(r => String(r.id)));\nconst goldCardIds = new Set(gold.map(r => String(r.card_id || '')));\n\nconst missingGold = card.filter(r => {\n  const id = String(r.id);\n  // 排除 buff 变体（后缀有 01, 02 等 2 位数的）\n  if (id.length >= 7 && /^\\d{7,}$/.test(id)) return false;\n  return !goldCardIds.has(id);\n});\n\nconsole.log('\\\\n=== Card 表中可能有独立价值但无金卡的（排除 buff 变体）===');\nmissingGold.forEach(r => console.log(`  ${r.id} - ${r.name || '??'} [type=${r.type}, rare=${r.rare}]`));\nconsole.log(`\\\\n共 ${missingGold.length} 个`);\n\n// 检查 CardGold 中是否有 card_id 等于这些变体 ID\nconst goldCardIdsSet = new Set(gold.map(r => String(r.card_id)));\nconst cardAllIds = [...new Set(card.map(r => String(r.id)))];\nconst extraCardIds = cardAllIds.filter(id => !goldCardIdsSet.has(id));\nconsole.log('\\\\n=== Card 存在但 CardGold 不存在的 Id（所有）===');\nconsole.log(extraCardIds.slice(0, 30).join(', '));\nconsole.log(`共 ${extraCardIds.length} 个`);\n\" 2>&1 | Out-String -Width 4096","timeout":15}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":1000,"output":1265,"cacheRead":136576,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":138841,"cost":{"input":0.00014000000000000001,"output":0.00035420000000000004,"cacheRead":0.003824128,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.004318328}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780303303020,"responseId":"0b2ab16c-85b3-4f7b-86a9-56d9d6a8ba7f"}}
