{"type":"message","id":"414a162d","parentId":"f6b14cee","timestamp":"2026-06-01T08:42:21.687Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I can see the CardSkin table clearly:\n\n- Row 1-4: Luban metadata headers\n- **Row 5**: Empty row (##var only, no data) - this is the \"null\" row my script found\n- Row 6-51: Actual data (46 rows)\n\nSo the \"empty type\" issue was just an empty separator row in the Excel, not a real data problem.\n\nLet me verify the CardSkin type references:\n\nRow 6: type=1050001 → Card has 1050001? Let me check...\nRow 25: type=1050001 but with no cardPool... yes same card reference.\nRow 20-22: type=2000097 → Card has 2000097 ✅\n\nAll skin type references should be to valid Card ids. Let me verify this quickly.\n\nActually, looking at my earlier results, the `readDataRows` function filtered `data.slice(4)` which would include Row 5 (the empty row). So the one \"empty type\" result was this empty separator row, not a real issue.\n\nLet me verify: from the earlier output:\n```\nCardSkin 发现 1 个问题:\n   [] type（映射卡牌）为空\n```\n\nThe `[]` means id was null which confirms it was the empty row (Row 5).\n\nSo the final results are:\n1. **CardGold.card_id** → ✅ 全部 515 条有效\n2. **CardSkin.type** → ✅ 全部 46 条数据有效（1条空行是 Excel 分隔符，不是数据）\n3. **Card 无金卡** → 56 个都是 buff 变体（`id` 末尾有两位后缀如 `01`），不是独立的卡牌实体","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"好了，全部排查清楚了！以下是检查结果：\n\n---\n\n## 📊 数据完整性检查报告\n\n### ✅ CardGold → Card 引用\n| 项目 | 结果 |\n|------|------|\n| CardGold 数据行 | 515 条 |\n| 引用错误（card_id 不存在于 Card 表） | **0 个 ✅** |\n| 全部 card_id 有效 | ✅ |\n\n### ✅ CardSkin → Card 引用\n| 项目 | 结果 |\n|------|------|\n| CardSkin 数据行 | 46 条 |\n| 引用错误（type 映射卡牌不存在于 Card 表） | **0 个 ✅** |\n| 1 个\"空 type\"是 Excel 第5行的空白分隔行，非数据行 | 已排除 ✅ |\n\n### 📌 补充信息：Card 无金卡（56个）\n全部 56 个都是 **buff 变体**（ID 以 2 位后缀结尾，如 `200009701`、`104000401`），本质上还是那张主卡的金卡。**不需要额外补录**。例如：\n- 灭世 → 主卡 `2000097` 已有金卡，变体 `200009701` 无需重复金卡\n- 白眼青龙 → 主卡 `1040004` 已有金卡\n- 疯狂科学家 → 主卡 `1050001` 已有金卡\n\n### 结论\n**CardGold 和 CardSkin 两张表都没有数据错位或引用不存在的 Card Id 问题。** ✅"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":1286,"output":705,"cacheRead":142080,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":144071,"cost":{"input":0.00018004000000000002,"output":0.0001974,"cacheRead":0.00397824,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00435568}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1780303334797,"responseId":"47ff74a0-2825-433c-9554-f728f18c148b"}}
