{"type":"message","id":"f7ac89c8","parentId":"482e2158","timestamp":"2026-06-01T09:04:05.657Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"OK, the images can't be analyzed directly due to the missing sharp dependency. Let me work with what I know from the text description:\n\n1. Player 3305439909 opened card packs on June 1, 2026 at 00:37\n2. The UI showed 2 copies of \"镜子魔女的化身\" (Mirror Witch's Incarnation) premium/alt art card\n3. But backpack only has 1 copy\n4. Server logs also only show 1 copy\n\nThe question is whether this is a front-end display issue.\n\nLet me look at the relevant configuration data to understand how this card works. Key things to check:\n\n1. **CardSkin table** - For \"镜子魔女的化身\" (id=510100431)\n   - type=1010043 → Card ID reference\n   - This is a skin card (异画 = alternate art)\n\n2. **Card table** - For id=1010043 (镜子魔女的化身)\n   \n3. **CardGold table** - For card_id=1010043\n\n4. **CardPool table** - To understand which card packs contain this card\n\n5. Check if there's any configuration about displaying duplicate premium cards\n\nThe core question: When the player opened the pack, the UI showed the same premium card appearing twice - is this because:\n- The card pack generation logic created two entries for the same card skin\n- The front-end display logic double-counted something\n- The CardPool/Card config has some duplication\n\nLet me look at the relevant config data.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"主人，图片我这里看不了（缺依赖）。但问题描述很清楚，我来查一下相关数据配置，看看是不是前端显示逻辑的问题。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_vNThZLYTiJrASMIv682n6151","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace; node scripts/check_skin_all_rows.mjs 2>&1 | Select-String \"510100431|1010043|镜子\"","timeout":10}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":320,"output":454,"cacheRead":141952,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":142726,"cost":{"input":