{"type":"message","id":"f40cb9c7","parentId":"ce12a01a","timestamp":"2026-06-01T09:04:15.290Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"OK so:\n- CardSkin id=510100431 → type=1010043 (镜子魔女的化身), cardPool=5\n- This skin belongs to card pool 5\n\nLet me look at the CardPool table to understand what card pool 5 contains, and also look at what the card pack opening flow looks like.\n\nActually, the key issue is about \"开出了2张镜子魔女的化身的异画卡\" - the player opened 2 copies of the same premium card from a pack. Let me investigate the CardPool and how premium cards are configured.\n\nLet me look at:\n1. CardPool table - what's in pool 5\n2. CardSkin table - check if there are multiple entries for type=1010043\n3. The card pack opening flow - maybe there's a configuration that causes duplicate display","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_esMCSCtAnO4H4n2gyLgG7160","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace; node -e \"\nimport XLSX from 'xlsx';\nimport path from 'path';\nconst DIR = 'E:\\\\Solo\\\\nightoffullmoon\\\\client\\\\config\\\\SoloConfig\\\\Datas';\nfunction readAll(fn) {\n  const data = XLSX.utils.sheet_to_json(XLSX.readFile(path.join(DIR, fn),{raw:true}).Sheets[0],{header:1,defval:null,raw:true});\n  const h = data[0]; const rows = data.slice(4).filter(r=>r.some(c=>c!=null&&c!=''));\n  return rows.map(r=>{const o={};h.forEach((h,i)=>{if(h&&h!=='##var')o[h]=r[i];});return o;});\n}\nconst card = readAll('Card.xlsx');\nconst skin = readAll('CardSkin.xlsx');\nconst pool = readAll('CardPool.xlsx');\nconst gold = readAll('CardGold.xlsx');\n\n// 查找 1010043 镜子魔女的化身 的卡牌信息\nconst cardInfo = card.filter(r => String(r.id) === '1010043');\nconsole.log('=== Card 1010043 镜子魔女的化身 ===');\ncardInfo.forEach(r => console.log('  type:', r.type, '| name:', r.name, '| cardPool:', r.cardPool, '| rare:', r.rare));\n\n// 查找所有 type=1010043 的皮肤\nconst skinMatches = skin.filter(r => String(r.type) === '1010043');\nconsole.log('\\n=== 所有 type=1010043 的 CardSkin ===');\nskinMatches.forEach(r => console.log('  id:', r.id, '| name:', r.name, '| cardPool:', r.cardPool, '| icon:', r.icon));\n\n// CardPool 5 的内容 - 注意 cardPool 字段在 gold 和 skin 中可能是 list, 需要按逗号分割\nconsole.log('\\n=== CardPool 5 中的卡牌 ===');\nconst pool5Cards = card.filter(r => {\n  const pools = String(r.cardPool || '').split(',').map(s => s.trim());\n  return pools.includes('5');\n});\nconsole.log('  Card 表中有', pool5Cards.length, '张卡属于 pool 5');\npool5Cards.slice(0, 10).forEach(r => console.log('  ', r.id, '-', r.name, 'rare:', r.rare));\n\n// CardPool 5 的皮肤\nconst pool5Skins = skin.filter(r => {\n  const pools = String(r.cardPool || '').split(',').map(s => s.trim());\n  return pools.includes('5');\n});\nconsole.log('\\n  CardSkin 表中有', pool5Skins.length, '张皮肤属于 pool 5');\npool5Skins.forEach(r => console.log('  ', r.type, '-', r.name, '-', r.id));\n\n// 检查 CardPool.xlsx 的定义\nconsole.log('\\n=== CardPool 定义 ===');\npool.slice(0, 5).forEach(r => console.log(' ', JSON.stringify(r)));\n\" 2>&1 | Out-String -Width 4096","timeout":15}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":55,"output":931,"cacheRead":142720,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":143706,"cost":{"input":0.0000077,"output":0.00026068,"cacheRead":0.0039961599999999995,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00426454}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780304646320,"responseId":"0981651e-6297-48ac-aea2-55a4fa6a42fe"}}
