{"type":"message","id":"26bdf9a3","parentId":"cbc2d66b","timestamp":"2026-06-01T09:04:33.534Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I can see the data structure. Let me look at the key pieces:\n\n1. **Card 1010043** (镜子魔女的化身):\n   - type: 1 (随从)\n   - name: 镜子魔女的化身\n   - cardPool: 5\n   - rare: 5 (橙色/传说)\n   - It has buff: \"101004301\"\n\n2. **CardPool** table:\n   - Pool 1 (id=1): \"旅途的开始\" - card_rarerate = weight table for different rarities\n   - Pool 2 (id=2): \"恶魔弥达斯\" \n   - Pool 3 (id=3): \"死神的低语\"\n   - Pool 4 (id=4): \"月下的狼影\"\n   - Pool 5 would contain the premium cards (异画)\n\nLet me look at what Pool 5 contains. From the skin data, skin cards with cardPool=5 include:\n- Row51: id=510100431 type=1010043 name=镜子魔女的化身 cardPool=5\n\nAnd from the CardSkin table, skins belonging to pool 5:\n- 镜子魔女的化身 (1010043) with skin id 510100431\n\nSo the skin \"镜子魔女的化身\" is in pool 5 (presumably a specific premium card pack).\n\nNow the issue is: the player opened a pack and saw 2 copies of this premium card. But the server only gave 1.\n\nThis could be:\n1. A front-end display bug where the animation/UI shows the same card twice\n2. The pack opening logic creates the same card ID twice in the displayed pack results\n\nLet me think about what the pack opening flow looks like. The player opens a card pack (pool 5). The pack contains multiple cards. When the pack opening animation shows the results, one of the displayed results is this premium card. The player says they saw 2 copies.\n\nThe server recorded only 1 copy. So the most likely explanation is:\n- The front-end double-counts or displays the same card twice in the UI\n- OR the pack data has the same card appearing multiple times in the pack result data\n\nLet me check if there are any other relevant data tables that might explain this. Let me check for any related configurations about how packs generate duplicate cards, or about how premium cards are handled.\n\nActually, looking at the data more carefully - the CardSkin table shows only ONE entry for type=1010043 (镜子魔女的化身). There aren't 2 different skins for the same card. So the issue is about one skin appearing twice in the UI.\n\nGiven that:\n1. Server log shows only 1 copy added → the backend logic is correct\n2. Player saw 2 copies → front-end display issue\n\nThis is likely a bug in the pack opening result display logic where the same card ID appears twice in the local pack result data. Let me check if there are any relevant Unity prefabs or scripts I should look at.\n\nActually, wait - the player said \"开出了2张镜子魔女的化身的异画卡\" - this could mean:\n(a) Two different skin cards that both are for \"镜子魔女的化身\"\n(b) The same skin card appearing twice in the display\n\nIf option (a), then the issue might be about the CardPool mapping or card generation logic creating duplicate entries.\n\nLet me look for the pack opening code to understand the flow. But first, let me check if there are TWO CardSkin entries for Card ID 1010043.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_puN69ORcBJ8az45Y4IUx8842","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace; node -e \"\nimport XLSX from 'xlsx';\nconst DIR = 'E:\\\\Solo\\\\nightoffullmoon\\\\client\\\\config\\\\SoloConfig\\\\Datas';\nfunction readAll(fn) {\n  const data = XLSX.utils.sheet_to_json(XLSX.readFile(DIR+'/'+fn,{raw:true}).Sheets[0],{header:1,defval:null,raw:true});\n  const h = data[0]; const rows = data.slice(4).filter(r=>r.some(c=>c!=null&&c!=''));\n  return rows.map(r=>{const o={};h.forEach((h,i)=>{if(h&&h!=='##var')o[h]=r[i];});return o;});\n}\nconst skin = readAll('CardSkin.xlsx');\n\n// 检查 type=1010043 的所有记录\nconst tgt = skin.filter(r => String(r.type) === '1010043');\nconsole.log('type=1010043 的 CardSkin:', tgt.length, '条');\ntgt.forEach(r => console.log('  id:', r.id, '| type:', r.type, '| name:', r.name, '| cardPool:', r.cardPool));\n\n// 检查所有 cardPool=5 的 CardSkin\nconst pool5Skins = skin.filter(r => String(r.cardPool || '').split(',').map(s=>s.trim()).includes('5'));\nconsole.log('\\\\ncardPool=5 的 CardSkin:', pool5Skins.length, '条');\npool5Skins.forEach(r => console.log('  id:', r.id, '| type:', r.type, '| name:', r.name, '| cardPool:', r.cardPool));\n\n// 看看这个玩家的相关服务器日志应该查什么\n// 检查 CardPool 表 5 的详细配置\nconst pool = readAll('CardPool.xlsx');\nconsole.log('\\\\n=== 所有 CardPool ===');\npool.forEach(r => console.log('  id:', r.id, '| type:', r.type, '| title:', r.title, '| packRange:', r.packRange));\n\" 2>&1 | Out-String -Width 4096","timeout":15}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":4967,"output":1285,"cacheRead":144384,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":150636,"cost":{"input":0.00069538,"output":0.0003598,"cacheRead":0.004042752,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.005097932}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780304661861,"responseId":"f7eb73ae-0ed5-4437-962e-4670314aaba2"}}
