{"type":"message","id":"3557f783","parentId":"15a56e6a","timestamp":"2026-06-01T09:05:15.813Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"OK so it works now! The issue in the previous script was that my readAll function was written differently. The data shows:\n\n1. CardSkin has 47 rows after mapping\n2. Mapped Row 0 = empty row (Excel row 5), which is the `##var` only row\n3. Mapped Row 1 = first actual data row (id=510500011, type=1050001)\n4. type=1010043 has exactly 1 match ✅\n\nSo there's only ONE CardSkin entry for 镜子魔女的化身 (id=510100431, type=1010043). This means the pack opening result showed the same skin twice, not two different skins.\n\nNow, let me think about what could cause this front-end display issue:\n\n1. The pack opening animation logic creates a list of [cardId, skinId?] pairs and renders them\n2. If the same card gets generated in the pack data BUT the skin card is treated as both a regular card AND a premium card at the same time, the UI might show it twice\n3. OR the data structure sent to the UI includes both a \"card_gold\" entry and a \"card_skin\" entry for the same card, and the UI incorrectly renders both as separate premium card results\n\nGiven that:\n- Server log shows only 1 card added\n- The issue was with 镜子魔女的化身 异画\n\nThe most likely cause is in the front-end pack opening display code. The card pack probably generated:\n- 1x 镜子魔女的化身 (as a regular card or as gold card)\n- 1x 镜子魔女的化身 异画 (as a premium card)\n\nAnd the UI showed them as two separate premium card reveals when it should have been one.\n\nLet me look for the pack opening Unity scripts to find the bug.\n\nActually, I don't really have a Unity project structure to look up. Let me search for relevant code files.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"Now I can read the data properly. Let me check if there are any other relevant configs and look at the pack opening code."},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_lsdqIvqOps1i1yiI3J4a8885","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"import XLSX from 'xlsx';\nconst DIR = 'E:\\\\Solo\\\\nightoffullmoon\\\\client\\\\config\\\\SoloConfig\\\\Datas';\n\nfunction readAll(fn) {\n  const data = XLSX.utils.sheet_to_json(XLSX.readFile(DIR+'/'+fn,{raw:true}).Sheets[0],{header:1,defval:null,raw:true});\n  const h = data[0]; const rows = data.slice(4);\n  return rows.map(row => {const o={};h.forEach((hdr,i)=>{if(hdr&&hdr!=='##var')o[hdr]=row[i];});return o;});\n}\n\n// CardSkin: type=1010043\nconst skin = readAll('CardSkin.xlsx');\nconst tgt = skin.filter(r => String(r.type) === '1010043');\nconsole.log('=== 镜子魔女的化身 皮肤 ===');\ntgt.forEach(r => console.log(JSON.stringify(r, null, 2)));\n\n// CardSkin: 所有替换特效 replacePlayEffect\nconsole.log('\\n=== replacePlayEffect 有值的 CardSkin ===');\nconst hasEffect = skin.filter(r => r.replacePlayEffect && Object.keys(r.replacePlayEffect).length > 0);\nconsole.log('共', hasEffect.length, '个');\n\n// CardPool 5 的详细配置 - 用 row-based 读取\nconst poolData = XLSX.utils.sheet_to_json(XLSX.readFile(DIR+'/CardPool.xlsx',{raw:true}).Sheets[0],{header:1,defval:null,raw:true});\nconsole.log('\\n=== CardPool 5 (异画池) ===');\nfor (let i = 4; i < poolData.length; i++) {\n  const r = poolData[i];\n  const id = r ? r[1] : null;\n  if (id === 5) {\n    console.log('Row', i+1, ':', JSON.stringify(r));\n  }\n}\n\n// 检查 CardGold 中 cardPool 相关的配置\nconst gold = readAll('CardGold.xlsx');\nconst gold1010043 = gold.filter(r => String(r.card_id) === '1010043');\nconsole.log('\\n=== CardGold 中 1010043 的金卡 ===');\ngold1010043.forEach(r => console.log(JSON.stringify(r)));\n","path":"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace\\scripts\\debug_pack_issue.mjs"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":872,"output":1024,"cacheRead":153728,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":155624,"cost":{"input":0.00012208,"output":0.00028672,"cacheRead":0.004304384,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.004713184}},"stopReason":"toolUse","time