{"type":"message","id":"179233f7","parentId":"f03edd52","timestamp":"2026-06-01T09:06:49.117Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The 周以天 cookie is valid until June 8. Let me check which cookies file the create_bug uses. From the skill, it says:\n```\nCookies file: workspace/tapd_cookies.json\n```\n\nBut from MEMORY.md:\n```\n### 两个账号\n- 周以天：提单用，cookie `tapd_cookies_zhouyitian.json`\n- 叶枝君：备用，cookie `tapd_cookies_yezhijun.json`\n- 主文件 `tapd_cookies.json` 保持为周以天（提单脚本默认读取）\n```\n\nSo the main `tapd_cookies.json` is 周以天's. Let me check if it exists and works.\n\nActually, let me just spawn the sub-agent with all the info needed.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_ul9Tgy1xdcry8yw4jsSv8578","name":"sessions_spawn","arguments":{"task":"在 TAPD 提一个 Bug 单。\n\n## Bug 信息\n- **标题：** 多卡包抽卡，橙卡出现多张显示问题\n- **描述：** 玩家3305439909在6月1日00:37开卡包时，开出了\"镜子魔女的化身\"的异画卡，界面上显示了2张，但背包（服务器日志）中只记录了1张。怀疑是开卡包UI在橙卡出现时的显示逻辑有bug——存在多卡包/多抽卡时，同一张高稀有度卡被UI重复渲染的问题。\n- **处理人：** 叶枝君（程序bug）\n- **抄送：** 周以天\n- **优先级：** P2\n- **发现版本：** 【1V1】正式版本V2.0\n- **模块：** 1V1\n- **研发分支：** YZY_1V1 V1.0 Beta\n- **附件：** 玩家的3张截图\n  - `C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\media\\inbound\\f2e3a109-61ad-457b-82c7-6bd66fe2f24a.jpg`\n  - `C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\media\\inbound\\816ac1ef-f6d1-4ecf-821f-17936ce57f4b.png`\n  - `C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\media\\inbound\\a4fddbb6-88c2-4323-9384-b45c54049395.jpg`\n\n## 操作\n1. 用 `import { createBug } from './scripts/create_bug.mjs'` 创建 bug\n2. Cookie 在 `workspace/tapd_cookies.json`（周以天的号，已验证有效到6月8日）\n3. 附件需先点击 `#upload-attachement` 触发器，然后 `setInputFiles` 上传\n4. 上传每个文件后等 6 秒\n5. 完成后把 Bug 链接发给我\n\n## 注意\n- 处理人和抄送用 autocomplete 方式输入\n- 附件上传完等6秒再提交\n- 完成后用 sessions_send 把结果发到 main session（主人是 Yousan 叶枝君）","mode":"run"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":171,"output":741,"cacheRead":163072,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":163984,"cost":{"input":0.0